\":2,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784212200,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":108992,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Mebius Dust\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Mebius Dust\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"メビウス・ダスト\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx108992-skuOsfmLmMd2.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx108992-skuOsfmLmMd2.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#50bbc9\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"On February 29, 2000, a group of Möbius meteorites fell down to earth. These meteorites brought new material called Möbius Dust, which dissolves in air and can cause miracles. The day the Möbius meteorites fell was dubbed 2.29, and the economic disparity in Japan increased dramatically after that day. A group of people fed up with the wealth inequality fought back with acts of terrorism. The police established a special group to fight against the terrorists and a school to train members for that group.\\\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003c/br\\u003e\\\\n(Sources: Comic Natalie, Live Chart)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":53,\\\"popularity\\\":6651,\\\"episodes\\\":null,\\\"duration\\\":null,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Action\\\",\\\"Supernatural\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":2,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784212200},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ByOF3FLlAws\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ByOF3FLlAws/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":415164,\\\"episode\\\":2,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784213760,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":196187,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Super no Ura de Yani Suu Futari\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Smoking Behind the Supermarket with You\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"スーパーの裏でヤニ吸うふたり\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196187-0dgFi2CPp3xn.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196187-0dgFi2CPp3xn.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#f1c9bb\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196187-Z9dV6uotmKjM.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"At age forty-five, office worker Sasaki has had enough of the corporate grind. His only solace is smoking-and the friendly smile of supermarket cashier Yamada. When Sasaki can't find Yamada after a particularly trying day, a striking woman invites him to smoke with her. The despondent man thinks he's made a new smoking buddy in the cool, teasing Tayama, but Sasaki doesn't realize he already knows her!\\\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Square Enix)\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n\\u003ci\\u003eNote: Episodes 1-6 had an early release by ABEMA and Crunchyroll on June 3rd, 2026 in a mini-episode batch format that splits 6 episodes into 12, ahead of the TV broadcast which started on July 9th, 2026.\\u003c/i\\u003e\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":83,\\\"popularity\\\":85823,\\\"episodes\\\":12,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Comedy\\\",\\\"Romance\\\",\\\"Slice of Life\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":2,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784213760},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"aOOwNK6Ul6E\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aOOwNK6Ul6E/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":408482,\\\"episode\\\":1,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784214000,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":206819,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Kimi to Hanabi to Yakusoku to\\\",\\\"english\\\":null,\\\"native\\\":\\\"君と花火と約束と\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206819-9VJOdSC6yFET.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206819-9VJOdSC6yFET.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#d6a178\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/206819-4oLkAimSr18r.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"The story centers on two Tokyo high schoolers who connect over a painting of fireworks. They trace the painting to the Nagaoka Fireworks Festival in Niigata, one of Japan's three major fireworks festivals, and to a mysterious promise that connects the two to the past.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News, edited) \\\\n\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":null,\\\"popularity\\\":4549,\\\"episodes\\\":1,\\\"duration\\\":null,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Romance\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"MOVIE\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":1,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784214000},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"zwiemWqog74\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zwiemWqog74/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":414952,\\\"episode\\\":4,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784214000,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":208044,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Rakudai Kenja no Gakuin Musou: Nidome no Tensei, S-Rank Cheat Majutsushi Bouken-roku\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"From Overshadowed to Overpowered: Second Reincarnation of a Talentless Sage\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"落第賢者の学院無双～二度目の転生、Sランクチート魔術師冒険録～\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx208044-Pm2UhvApQFUh.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx208044-Pm2UhvApQFUh.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#f1d61a\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Ephtal is reincarnated as a human, coming from modern Earth. In this new world where magic is real, he decides to devote the entirety of his life in the pursuit of magic. Despite his efforts, though, he discovers that he is absolutely talentless in magic, and breathed his last in anguish....But it isn't the end for him just yet! He reincarnates once again bearing the same name, Ephtal, 400 years later. Having retained his knowledge and power, he steals his resolve and once again sets his sights for the peak of magic!\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n(Source: Comikey)\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n\\u003ci\\u003eNote: Rakudai Kenja no Gakuin Musou: Nidome no Tensei, S-Rank Cheat Majutsushi Bouken-roku is streaming a week in advance of the TV broadcast on dAnimeStore, ABEMA, U-NEXT, and Anime Hodai beginning June 26th, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 2nd, 2026.\\u003c/i\\u003e\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":66,\\\"popularity\\\":30391,\\\"episodes\\\":null,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Action\\\",\\\"Adventure\\\",\\\"Fantasy\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"ONA\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":4,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784214000},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"QOeItd-RrVs\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QOeItd-RrVs/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":416988,\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784215560,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":180136,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Tsuihou Sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou Suru\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"The Exiled Heavy Knight Knows How to Game the System\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"追放された転生重騎士はゲーム知識で無双する\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx180136-gtMTCRlOD4OE.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx180136-gtMTCRlOD4OE.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#50c9fe\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Born into a prestigious family of master swordsmen, Elymas Edvaughn’s future shatters when he awakens the so-called “defective” Heavy Knight class. Disowned and cast out, he regains memories of another life—and realizes this world mirrors a VR game he once mastered. Armed with knowledge no one else possesses, he sets out to rewrite his fate and prove the strength of the “weakest” class.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":67,\\\"popularity\\\":37669,\\\"episodes\\\":26,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Action\\\",\\\"Fantasy\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784215560},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"uC13b3_8riU\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uC13b3_8riU/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":412632,\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784215800,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":207141,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Yani Neko\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Chainsmoker Cat\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"ヤニねこ\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207141-h5q5KJPd6vaX.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207141-h5q5KJPd6vaX.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#50a1f1\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207141-MvHAS2YVfJzL.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Yani is a catgirl with a seriously bad smoking habit. She smokes so much that her apartment smells like ash and is littered with cigarette butts—and plenty of other trash! Every time she tries to quit, she becomes weak to the cravings and gives in almost instantly. Will she ever get her life together, or is she doomed to live as a chainsmoking slob forever? \\\\n\\u003cBR\\u003e\\u003cBR\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":68,\\\"popularity\\\":43515,\\\"episodes\\\":null,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Comedy\\\",\\\"Slice of Life\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784215800},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"KYGgyQtSAdI\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KYGgyQtSAdI/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":414963,\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784219280,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":204466,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Otome Kaijuu Caramelise\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"KAIJU GIRL CARAMELISE\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"乙女怪獣キャラメリゼ\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204466-vXMvIs4VOoQd.png\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204466-vXMvIs4VOoQd.png\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#e45d78\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204466-cpbNGN9qHrGP.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Kuroe Akaishi just wants a normal high school life—but that’s impossible with a rare condition that turns her into a giant kaiju whenever her emotions spike! Things get even worse when she falls for Arata Minami, the most popular boy in class. Now every blush, heartbeat, and crush could trigger a monster transformation. Can Kuroe survive high school love before it destroys everything around her?!\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":75,\\\"popularity\\\":24247,\\\"episodes\\\":null,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Comedy\\\",\\\"Romance\\\",\\\"Supernatural\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784219280},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ECtHlHde3EQ\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ECtHlHde3EQ/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdul