gAt\\\":1784394000,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":199066,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Hanaori-san wa Tensei Shite mo Kenka ga Shitai\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Hanaori-san Still Wants to Fight in the Next Life\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"花織さんは転生しても喧嘩がしたい\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199066-YXDVsguvFZMm.jpg\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199066-YXDVsguvFZMm.jpg\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#43bbe4\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Once the Demon King, now a shut-in NEET—Ryuusei Narukami’s second life is anything but peaceful! When Meteor Hanaori, the Hero who once defeated him, suddenly returns as a normal high school girl, his world is thrown into chaos. Determined to change, Ryuusei reenters society as a teacher and ends up teaching at her school! Their explosive reunion reignites the past—and sparks an unexpected love!\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":66,\\\"popularity\\\":12373,\\\"episodes\\\":null,\\\"duration\\\":null,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Comedy\\\",\\\"Romance\\\",\\\"Supernatural\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":2,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784394000},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"xueZbCyZcnI\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xueZbCyZcnI/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":414267,\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784396280,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":201514,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Saijo no Osewa: Takane no Hanadarake na Meimonkou de, Gakuin Ichi no Ojou-sama (Seikatsu Nouryoku Kaimu) wo Kagenagara Osewa suru Koto ni Narimashita\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Rich Girl Caretaker: I'm Secretly the Caregiver of the Most Popular Girl in This Rich Kid School\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"才女のお世話 高嶺の花だらけな名門校で、学院一のお嬢様(生活能力皆無)を陰ながらお世話することになりました\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx201514-BHAeWhSbcBrT.png\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx201514-BHAeWhSbcBrT.png\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#e48650\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Hinako Konohana is the perfect young lady—graceful, elegant, and flawless… or so everyone thinks. Behind closed doors, she’s a total disaster who can’t handle basic chores! When ordinary student Itsuki Tomonari becomes her caretaker, he’s thrown into 24/7 damage control, maintaining her “perfect” image. It’s awkward, nonstop chaos—but it starts softening into something that feels like love…\\\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\\",\\\"averageScore\\\":72,\\\"popularity\\\":25586,\\\"episodes\\\":12,\\\"duration\\\":24,\\\"genres\\\":[\\\"Comedy\\\",\\\"Romance\\\"],\\\"format\\\":\\\"TV\\\",\\\"season\\\":\\\"SUMMER\\\",\\\"seasonYear\\\":2026,\\\"status\\\":\\\"RELEASING\\\",\\\"nextAiringEpisode\\\":{\\\"episode\\\":3,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784396280},\\\"trailer\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JoRr4dfpXIU\\\",\\\"site\\\":\\\"youtube\\\",\\\"thumbnail\\\":\\\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JoRr4dfpXIU/hqdefault.jpg\\\"},\\\"isAdult\\\":false}},{\\\"id\\\":410592,\\\"episode\\\":15,\\\"airingAt\\\":1784412000,\\\"media\\\":{\\\"id\\\":204269,\\\"title\\\":{\\\"romaji\\\":\\\"Odekake Kozame Season 2\\\",\\\"english\\\":\\\"Little Shark's Day Out Season 2\\\",\\\"native\\\":\\\"おでかけ子ザメ シーズン2\\\"},\\\"coverImage\\\":{\\\"extraLarge\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204269-fTR4iyVjTHiC.png\\\",\\\"large\\\":\\\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204269-fTR4iyVjTHiC.png\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#50bbfe\\\"},\\\"bannerImage\\\":null,\\\"description\\\":\\\"Second season of \\u003ci\\u003eOdekake Kozame\\u003c/i\\u003e.\\\",\\\"averageSc