}]}]}],null]}]\n22:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"theme-color\",\"content\":\"#141310\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"name\":\"color-scheme\",\"content\":\"dark\"}]]\n25:I[86869,[],\"IconMark\"]\n1f:null\n24:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Airing Schedule | Otaku Insider\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Weekly anime airing schedule. See exactly when new episodes drop, in your local time.\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"2\",{\"rel\":\"manifest\",\"href\":\"/manifest.webmanifest\",\"crossOrigin\":\"$undefined\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"name\":\"generator\",\"content\":\"v0.app\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Airing Schedule | Otaku Insider\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Weekly anime airing schedule. See exactly when new episodes drop, in your local time.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:image\",\"content\":\"http://localhost:3000/opengraph-image?b11afcff612a52f4\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":\"og:image:type\",\"content\":\"image/png\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"8\",{\"property\":\"og:image:width\",\"content\":\"1200\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"9\",{\"property\":\"og:image:height\",\"content\":\"630\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"10\",{\"property\":\"og:image:alt\",\"content\":\"Otaku Insider — Your ultimate anime companion\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"11\",{\"name\":\"twitter:card\",\"content\":\"summary_large_image\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"12\",{\"name\":\"twitter:title\",\"content\":\"Airing Schedule | Otaku Insider\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"13\",{\"name\":\"twitter:description\",\"content\":\"Weekly anime airing schedule. See exactly when new episodes drop, in your local time.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"14\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image\",\"content\":\"http://localhost:3000/opengraph-image?b11afcff612a52f4\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"15\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image:alt\",\"content\":\"Otaku Insider — Your ultimate anime companion\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"16\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image:type\",\"content\":\"image/png\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"17\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image:width\",\"content\":\"1200\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"18\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image:height\",\"content\":\"630\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"19\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/logo.jpg\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"20\",{\"rel\":\"apple-touch-icon\",\"href\":\"/logo.jpg\"}],[\"$\",\"$L25\",\"21\",{}]]\n26:I[78477,[\"8500\",\"static/chunks/8500-f62a38ff68ab7f42.js\",\"7826\",\"static/chunks/app/schedule/page-d5f66d9e5a509eab.js\"],\"ScheduleView\"]\n27:T462,The year is 2029. In near-future Japan, where the world has become highly information-intensive, with a vast corporate network covering the planet, electrons and light pulsing through it. But the nation-state and ethnic groups still survive.  <br><br> Motoko Kusanagi, a full-body cyborg, leads an elite combat unit, including Batou. While commanding her team, Kusanagi envisions the creation of a specialized task force to preemptively strike against emerging threats. Meanwhile, Daisuke Aramaki of the Ministry of Internal Affairs, who had been planning to establish a similar unit, recruited Kusanagi and her team. Together, they begin operations as Public Security Section 9—an offensive tactical unit known as “Shell Squad.” As they confront complex cybercrimes and international conspiracies, the existence of a mysterious, unidentified hacker known as The “Puppet Master” emerges on the horizon of their investigation. <br><br> What fate awaits Kusanagi? And what is the Puppet Master’s true objective? A new era of cyberpunk action begins.  <br><br>\n(Source:攻殻機動隊 THE GHOST IN THE SHELL Site)28:T431,“I will become the world’s most wonderful maid!” <br><br>\nWith her skirt fluttering in black and white, the girl shouted. Her name is Melody. A reincarnated former Japanese girl, she now pursues her dream in her new life, working as an all-purpose maid for a poor count’s family in the kingdom of Théolas. When she makes it, even cheap tea turns into a luxury brew, and a dilapidated mansion is quickly restored to new! Cleaning, serving, hunting, DIY—leave it all to her and her powerful magic. Unbeknownst to Melody, this world is actually an otome game, and she is the most powerful and invincible heroine, the saint! Yet, she remains oblivious to this fact. Romance with handsome men? Attacks by the Demon Lord? Work comes first! A fantasy of misunderstood work that unknowingly shatters destiny!<br><br>\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)<br><br>\n\n<i>Note: Heroine? Seijo? Iie, All Works Maid desu (Ko)! is streaming a week in advance of the TV broadcast on dAnimeStore and ABEMA beginning June 24th, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 1st, 2026.</i>29:T4cc,Kudo Shinichi is a seventeen year-old high school detective whom people call the \"Modern Sherlock Holmes.\" However, one night after a date with his childhood sweetheart, Ran, Shinichi witnessed an illegal trade and, caught off his guard, was knocked unconscious and fed a drug that was supposed to kill him... but he woke up and found himself shrunken to a seven year-old. In order to track down the men who did this to him, Shinichi hid his identity and lived with Ran, whose father happened to be a hopeless detective, and with that came a series of murders and mysteries that he must solve. <br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)\n<br><br>\n<i>Note:<br>\n- Includes Keisatsu Gakkou-hen - Wild Police Story in episodes 1029, 1038, 1042, 1061<br>\n- Episodes 11, 52, 76, 118, 162, 184, 208, 342, 356, 449, 452, 487, 488, 489, 490, 515, 516, 521, 522, 651, 734, 804, 805, 927, 928, 1187 aired with a runtime of ~50 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.<br>\n- Episodes 96, 129, 174, 219, 263, 304, 383, 479 aired with a runtime of ~90 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.<br>\n- Episode 345, 425 aired with a runtime of ~115 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.<br>\n</i>2a:T406,Thirty years ago, the world was nearly destroyed by the sudden appearance of unknown \"invasive alien species.\"\n<br><br>\nHumans and these “invasive species” continue to vie for living space, and while humanity’s safety is currently barely secured, the world could be destroyed at any moment. Living in fear of death and destruction, people go about their daily lives as if trying to avert their eyes from danger and disaster.\n<br><br>\nIn this world, the United Nations Hazardous Species Investigation Agency, \"EXCEEDS,\" has begun operations to ward off crises and disasters caused by invasive species.\n<br><br>\nThe story begins on the island nation of \"Mizuho\" in the Far East. Shina Hisase is a young invasive species extermination hunter living on a remote island. What incident will befall Shina, who wishes only to live quietly with her younger sister Setsuna, her sole remaining family member?\n<br><br>\n<i>Note: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~48 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.</i>2b:T493,The novel takes place in the summer of 1907, the 40th year of the Meiji era. 15-year-old Inako Momokawa lives in the Fushimi area of Kyoto, and is the second daughter of a sake brewer. Nothing she does ever comes out right, and she receives a scolding from her father every day. Her only relief is the trust she places in her prayers to the gods. One day while at Fushimi Inari shrine, she meets a freewheeling young man named Kihachi Sakamoto. He rejects the gods, and boasts of the incoming age of electricity. <br><br>\n\nThe topic of marriage suddenly comes up in Inako's household. Her father is one-sidedly making all the decisions for her, and Inako is about to give up hope. It is then that Kihachi draws out Inako's true feelings of wanting to run away from her family. The only way to stop her marriage is to find an unusual book called the \"Electricity Catalog.\" The book is a prediction book about electricity that Kihachi wrote when he was a child, but his older brother Seiroku took the book, and its current whereabouts are unknown. Inako and Kihachi together go in search of the book across Kyoto and Shiga prefectures.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)2c:T644,Gold Roger was known as the Pirate King, the strongest and most infamous being to have sailed the Grand Line. The capture and death of Roger by the World Government brought a change throughout the world. His last words before his death revealed the location of the greatest treasure in the world, One Piece. It was this revelation that brought about the Grand Age of Pirates, men who dreamed of finding One Piece (which promises an unlimited amount of riches and fame), and quite possibly the most coveted of titles for the person who found it, the title of the Pirate King.<br><br>\nEnter Monkey D. Luffy, a 17-year-old boy that defies your standard definition of a pirate. Rather than the popular persona of a wicked, hardened, toothless pirate who ransacks villages for fun, Luffy’s reason for being a pirate is one of pure wonder; the thought of an exciting adventure and meeting new and intriguing people, along with finding One Piece, are his reasons of becoming a pirate. Following in the footsteps of his childhood hero, Luffy and his crew travel across the Grand Line, experiencing crazy adventures, unveiling dark mysteries and battling strong enemies, all in order to reach One Piece.<br><br>\n<b>*This includes the following special episodes:</b><br>\n- Chopperman to the Rescue! Protect the TV Station by the Shore! (Episode 336)<br>\n- The Strongest Tag-Team! Luffy and Toriko's Hard Struggle! (Episode 492)<br>\n- Team Formation! Save Chopper (Episode 542)<br>\n- History's Strongest Collaboration vs. Glutton of the Sea (Episode 590)<br>\n- 20th Anniversary! Special Romance Dawn (Episode 907)1c:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-8 flex flex-col gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance\",\"children\":\"Airing Schedule\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"New episodes airing over the next 7 days, shown in your local time.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"$L26\",null,{\"schedules\":[{\"id\":408343,\"episode\":398,\"airingAt\":1783994400,\"media\":{\"id\":155723,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Wushen Zhuzai: Da Wei Pian\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"武神主宰 大威篇\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx155723-hM261Imc5yfd.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx155723-hM261Imc5yfd.png\",\"color\":\"#c9f1f1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Wushen Zhuzai</i>.\",\"averageScore\":65,\"popularity\":565,\"episodes\":448,\"duration\":7,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":399,\"airingAt\":1784426400},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415229,\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1783994400,\"media\":{\"id\":213188,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jueshi Zhan Hun 2\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"绝世战魂 第2季\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213188-zwmmMVqqUjh8.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213188-zwmmMVqqUjh8.png\",\"color\":\"#f1e4c9\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In the Canglan Continent, strength is determined by martial spirits. Qin Nan, the young master of the Qin family, was originally a useless soul, suffering endless scorn. By chance, he awakened the soul of an ancient war god, thus defying fate. He swept through sect geniuses, overcame powerful enemies and obstacles, encountered a soulmate, used his battle spirit to break all laws, and forged a legend with his blood. From a humble young master, he rose through the ranks to become an invincible supreme celestial being who shakes the nine realms.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: IQIYI, translated)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":65,\"episodes\":100,\"duration\":10,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1784599200},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413488,\"episode\":12,\"airingAt\":1784001600,\"media\":{\"id\":211270,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Fei Ren Zai 3 Part 2\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"非人哉 第三季 第二部分\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx211270-JL9g9jogYvl2.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx211270-JL9g9jogYvl2.png\",\"color\":\"#e4a15d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The third season part two of <i>Fei Ren Zai.</i>\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":69,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":7,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"FINISHED\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":null,\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Yrz4cYTslJo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Yrz4cYTslJo/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416637,\"episode\":7,\"airingAt\":1784001600,\"media\":{\"id\":213484,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Bai Ri Cheng Wang\",\"english\":\"Crowned in a Hundred Days\",\"native\":\"百日成王\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213484-FIyYH43ASHgB.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213484-FIyYH43ASHgB.png\",\"color\":\"#1a86f1\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/213484-Apezw4iSrrr6.jpg\",\"description\":\"Driven to the brink of despair, restaurant owner Ming forms an unlikely bond with the soul of the true King Lie after swallowing it to save his loved one. Bound together by fate, the two embark on a perilous journey to challenge the tyrant who has usurped the throne.<br><br>\\nWith only one hundred days to change their destiny, Ming uses his extraordinary memory to master long-lost magic, gathering allies and winning the support of the people along the way. As their strength grows, so does their resolve to overthrow a corrupt regime, reclaim the rightful king's throne, and restore peace to the realm.<br><br>\\n(Source: Bilibili TV)\",\"averageScore\":60,\"popularity\":1629,\"episodes\":25,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1784260800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"IYcGvpXYfGE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IYcGvpXYfGE/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415675,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784028600,\"media\":{\"id\":128757,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tai-Ari deshita.: Ojou-sama wa Kakutou Game nante Shinai\",\"english\":\"Young Ladies Don't Play Fighting Games\",\"native\":\"対ありでした。 ～お嬢さまは格闘ゲームなんてしない～\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx128757-Iqc6hTjEYIz4.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128757-Iqc6hTjEYIz4.png\",\"color\":\"#436bff\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Mitsuki Aya has one goal at the elite Kuromi Girls’ Academy: to become a refined young lady like the school’s flawless “White Lily,” Yorue Mio. But her image of Mio shatters when Aya accidentally catches her...playing fighting games?! Turns out, the elegant Mio is actually a hardcore gamer—and she wants to duel Aya! The battle (and their friendship) begins.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":72,\"popularity\":19163,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784633400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"5PAsOIcot7I\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5PAsOIcot7I/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417334,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784032200,\"media\":{\"id\":187260,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kimi ga Shinu made Koi wo Shitai\",\"english\":\"I Want to Love You Till Your Dying Day\",\"native\":\"きみが死ぬまで恋をしたい\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187260-WW5RBa5NINRP.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187260-WW5RBa5NINRP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4ae35\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187260-HMkLPy3ZvzW1.jpg\",\"description\":\"At the mysterious orphanage where Sheena lives, death is nothing new to its residents—girls who no longer have families of their own, who are raised as weapons of war, taught to kill and take the lives of others without batting an eye. Everyone, that is, except Sheena, who wishes for nothing more than the growing conflict around her to end. On the night of her roommate's death, Sheena meets a strange girl covered in blood, who smiles despite the turmoil surrounding them. The next day, the girl appears as a new student in Sheena's class and introduces herself as Mimi. Initially thought to be a school myth, there are now whispers in the orphanage's halls that Mimi is their secret weapon—an immortal who cannot die. When Mimi is later assigned as Sheena's new roommate, Sheena's world grows even more complicated when she begins living with someone who loves and welcomes death, when all Sheena wants to do is stop it…\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"averageScore\":75,\"popularity\":38905,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784637000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"zJLbfK_9ZmQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zJLbfK_9ZmQ/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417360,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784033700,\"media\":{\"id\":213665,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Migawari Reijou wo Sukutta no wa Reikoku Mujihi na Koori no Ouji no Ai deshita\",\"english\":\"Saved By the Ice Cold Prince's Embrace\",\"native\":\"身代わり令嬢を救ったのは冷酷無慈悲な氷の王子の愛でした\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213665-E6byznDKrKY0.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213665-E6byznDKrKY0.png\",\"color\":\"#1aaee4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"As the illegitimate daughter of a count and his maid, Katrina was born into miserable circumstances. And now that she's lost her mother, the treatment from her stepsister and stepmother the countess has only grown worse. One day, her stepsister receives a royal order to move to the northern outskirts due to her unseemly behavior at a recent party. There, she is to learn proper conduct under the tutelage of the resident prince, rumored to be a cruel man. Not wanting to subject her daughter to such punishment, the countess decides to send Katrina instead. Katrina arrives in the north shaking in fear. But contrary to the stories, the \\\"merciless and cold-hearted\\\" prince is kinder than she believed. Might the pure-hearted Katrina find love in the wintry countryside?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":1221,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784638500},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Q3zyZrf3uyY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q3zyZrf3uyY/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414939,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784034000,\"media\":{\"id\":196219,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mujikaku Seijo wa Kyou mo Muishiki ni Chikara wo Tare Nagasu\",\"english\":\"The Oblivious Saint Can't Contain Her Power\",\"native\":\"無自覚聖女は今日も無意識に力を垂れ流す\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196219-imvC0rbk4VzH.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196219-imvC0rbk4VzH.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196219-2F64WTRfqRU9.jpg\",\"description\":\"Lady Carolina, the overlooked daughter of a powerful duke, has always believed herself to be the black sheep amid her illustrious kin. Her father is the distinguished prime minister; her elder sister, a prodigious mage destined to become their nation’s next Saint. In comparison, Carolina resigns herself to a quiet existence in their shadows until a sudden and unexpected royal decree alters her destiny, thrusting her into a political marriage with the formidable “Bloodthirsty Prince” of the neighboring Empire of Malcosias. Determined to prove her worth, Carolina takes a bold step into a world fraught with both political and mortal peril. As royal obligations intertwine with hints of true love and the stirrings of her own latent power, Carolina moves ever closer to understanding what it truly means to be exceptional.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"averageScore\":63,\"popularity\":13133,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784638800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"R82wqxOXPIM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/R82wqxOXPIM/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413692,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784037600,\"media\":{\"id\":177699,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Koukaku Kidoutai: THE GHOST IN THE SHELL\",\"english\":\"THE GHOST IN THE SHELL\",\"native\":\"攻殻機動隊 THE GHOST IN THE SHELL\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177699-hnzc1CS5ZSM2.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177699-hnzc1CS5ZSM2.png\",\"color\":null},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/177699-5kDbvDBhtSE3.jpg\",\"description\":\"$27\",\"averageScore\":78,\"popularity\":35343,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Psychological\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784642400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"b_v0-RWLo18\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/b_v0-RWLo18/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414465,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784039400,\"media\":{\"id\":209800,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yoroi Shinden Samurai Troopers Part 2\",\"english\":\"Yoroi-Shinden Samurai Troopers Cour 2\",\"native\":\"鎧真伝サムライトルーパー 第2クール\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx209800-v3TIdNz1AV0X.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx209800-v3TIdNz1AV0X.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4a143\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second part of <i>Yoroi Shinden Samurai Troopers</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":1041,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784644200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OKEoQo3cGVg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OKEoQo3cGVg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414661,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784041200,\"media\":{\"id\":198709,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tefuda ga Oome no Victoria\",\"english\":\"Victoria of Many Faces\",\"native\":\"手札が多めのビクトリア\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198709-3PFLvU6eqPvf.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198709-3PFLvU6eqPvf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In an age when spies act behind the scenes in every land, Chloe spends her days successfully carrying out even the most difficult missions due to her unparalleled disguise skills and martial arts abilities. After the betrayal of her boss, she suddenly disappears—as Chloe plans to redo her life as the ordinary citizen Victoria in the neighboring kingdom of Ashberry, striving for a “normal” life. However, Victoria's peaceful life is abruptly cut short as she begins to get involved with many people. In this new land, her experiences and abilities from her days as a spy come in far more useful than she ever expected! On the other hand, the second prince--and others--take an interest in Victoria's strength, and the shadows close in on the woman with many faces…\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":9188,\"episodes\":9,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784646000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"dm8QPSlRYdI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dm8QPSlRYdI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414242,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784046900,\"media\":{\"id\":207809,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sora wa Akai Kawa no Hotori\",\"english\":\"Red River\",\"native\":\"天は赤い河のほとり\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207809-cpS7CAyjN7iP.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207809-cpS7CAyjN7iP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4bb5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"After a mysterious hand drags her beneath a puddle, modern Japanese teenager Yuri awakens in the Hittite Empire of the 14th century BCE. Thrust into a deadly struggle for the throne, she joins Prince Kail to battle assassins, outwit royal conspiracies, and survive a world at war. As her exploits earn her renown as the goddess Ishtar, Yuri must choose between her old life and an uncertain future.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":61,\"popularity\":7753,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784651700},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"qpFcQ1Bek08\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qpFcQ1Bek08/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416107,\"episode\":28,\"airingAt\":1784070000,\"media\":{\"id\":204656,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"mofusand\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"mofusand\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg\",\"color\":\"#c9e443\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204656-ECYkRJKBxTLj.jpg\",\"description\":\"Shark Meow is an orange tabby kitty who wears a shark suit.<br>\\nA little clumsy and always taking things at their own cozy pace,<br>\\nbut every day with their best kitty friends — and the rescued baby kitty, Little Meow —<br>\\nis filled with unexpected little mishaps and sweet adventures.<br><br>\\n \\nA sunny warm spot in the park, the sparkle of the sea,<br>\\nsteam rising from freshly roasted sweet potatoes,<br>\\nthe fluttery feeling of the first snowfall…<br>\\nThese small everyday moments fill their world with warmth and delight.\\n <br><br>\\nYou can’t help but smile and think, “So true!”<br>\\nA soft and snuggly kitty anime that brings joy to everyday moments.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: QTORY Channel)\",\"averageScore\":60,\"popularity\":789,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":1,\"genres\":[\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":28,\"airingAt\":1784070000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Svh_xgdMWlU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Svh_xgdMWlU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415999,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784077200,\"media\":{\"id\":212309,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Transformers: Wild King W\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"トランスフォーマー ワイルドキングW\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx212309-gDqt6qz1RPEL.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx212309-gDqt6qz1RPEL.png\",\"color\":\"#3593e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"A sequel to <i>Transformers: Wild King</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":117,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":4,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Mecha\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784077200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"6gyPgg1YdYg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6gyPgg1YdYg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415493,\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1784080800,\"media\":{\"id\":213297,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yun Shen Buzhi Meng Special: Zhu Ming Zhi Yi\",\"english\":\"Eclipse of Illusion SP: The Miasma War\",\"native\":\"云深不知梦 特别篇：逐冥之役\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213297-hmYPfAXgQQDp.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213297-hmYPfAXgQQDp.jpg\",\"color\":\"#bbd6f1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In the primordial apocalypse, Xihe, a maiden of the Huihua Clan, fled the brutal rebellion in her ancestral homeland. Breaking free from the control of the Qiongming Demon Tribe, she embarks on a quest for the Demonslayer Divine Sword, igniting the War of the Six Armies.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":97,\"episodes\":6,\"duration\":22,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1784080800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416941,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784084400,\"media\":{\"id\":213703,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jiaonang Jihua: Qiji\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"胶囊计划 奇迹\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213703-ghO1AqW0bdaN.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213703-ghO1AqW0bdaN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb0d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"\\\"Capsules Project\\\" is a collection of domestically produced animated short films created by a professional team with mature animation production experience. With the creative theme of \\\"extreme emotion + independent theme,\\\" it does not restrict the creative form, exploring the possibilities of animation together with the team. The aim is to collaboratively create original short films with diverse styles and characteristics, and to help Chinese animators reach the world stage. \\\"Miracle\\\" represents transcending conventions and breaking through limitations to achieve extraordinary success, often accompanied by a sense of mystery that inspires awe and curiosity. What miracles will occur in these 10 stories?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":41,\"episodes\":8,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784084400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"XvuUOmNUtxc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XvuUOmNUtxc/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415968,\"episode\":10,\"airingAt\":1784103300,\"media\":{\"id\":163793,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Cheongchun Blossom: Uriui Bom\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"청춘블라썸 : 우리의 봄\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163793-dOI9QEcIrgBS.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163793-dOI9QEcIrgBS.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45d93\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Oh, to be young and in love. Oh, to be wild and carefree. The springtime of life is intense, tumultuous, and at times, oh so confusing. Spring, summer, fall and winter -- love blossoms in all seasons.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: WEBTOON)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":3625,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":15,\"genres\":[\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":10,\"airingAt\":1784103300},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413528,\"episode\":40,\"airingAt\":1784113200,\"media\":{\"id\":188529,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi\",\"english\":\"Cat Tales\",\"native\":\"うごく！ねこむかしばなし\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e46b5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"What if cats appeared in that story…? When beloved old tales and fairy stories are joined by cats, a surreal and heartwarming new adventure begins…!? Tabby cats, orange cats, calico cats, and white cats— a delightful mix of feline friends woven into timeless stories is sure to soothe the hearts of all humanity! A charming cat comedy is about to unfold!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: AniOne Asia)\",\"averageScore\":52,\"popularity\":541,\"episodes\":50,\"duration\":3,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":40,\"airingAt\":1784113200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"n-jg8syMe08\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n-jg8syMe08/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417384,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784116800,\"media\":{\"id\":198946,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Clevatess II: Majuu no Ou to Itsuwari no Yuusha Denshou\",\"english\":\"Clevatess Season 2\",\"native\":\"クレバテスⅡ-魔獣の王と偽りの勇者伝承-\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198946-IGXmbqBEYRYD.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198946-IGXmbqBEYRYD.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Clevatess: Majuu no Ou to Akago to Kabane no Yuusha</i>.\",\"averageScore\":75,\"popularity\":30646,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784116800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"0N1-8XY_3Rs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0N1-8XY_3Rs/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414761,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784118600,\"media\":{\"id\":135865,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Youjo Senki II\",\"english\":\"Saga of Tanya the Evil Season 2\",\"native\":\"幼女戦記Ⅱ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx135865-T7XIPMAbqcxN.png\",\"large\":\"http