999の村人\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx197715-KLFLxU24U1uL.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx197715-KLFLxU24U1uL.png\",\"color\":\"#5daef1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In Earthclear, everyone is born into a fixed role, and villagers are the weakest of all. Most never rise above Level 5—except Kouji Kagami, who is Level…999?! On a monster hunt, he meets Alice, the Demon King’s daughter, and discovers they share an impossible dream: coexistence between humans and demons. In a world destined for conflict, they charge into battle to defy fate and shatter the rules.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":64,\"popularity\":25580,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784127600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"YfWJLXcN7hI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YfWJLXcN7hI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417410,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784127600,\"media\":{\"id\":213961,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Youjo Shenki 2\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"ようじょしぇんき2\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b213961-x2ZvvtkYSTC9.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b213961-x2ZvvtkYSTC9.png\",\"color\":\"#f1d693\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Youjo Shenki</i>.<br><br>\\n\\nChibi parody of Youjo Senki.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":444,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784127600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"3yILla1h1pM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3yILla1h1pM/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415555,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784130240,\"media\":{\"id\":207254,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Thunder 3\",\"english\":\"Thunder 3\",\"native\":\"サンダー３\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207254-StcuNpmZTDCL.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207254-StcuNpmZTDCL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#1a93e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Three ordinary schoolboys come into possession of a DVD that supposedly opens a gateway to a parallel universe, but when their backs are turned Pyontaro's little sister Futaba passes through and gets kidnapped by the aliens that have overrun that version of Earth! Discovering that their cartoonish bodies make them supermen in the hyper-realistic parallel universe, the boys set out to rescue Futaba.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Kodansha USA)\",\"averageScore\":50,\"popularity\":1363,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784130240},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"wsb07srXk_M\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wsb07srXk_M/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417041,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784131200,\"media\":{\"id\":209669,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hanazakari no Kimitachi e 2nd Season\",\"english\":\"Hana-Kimi Season 2\",\"native\":\"花ざかりの君たちへ 第2期\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx209669-7GlPe2ra5f1i.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx209669-7GlPe2ra5f1i.jpg\",\"color\":\"#436be4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Hanazakari no Kimitachi e</i>.\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Hanazakari no Kimitachi e 2nd Season is streaming 1 week in advance of the TV broadcast on Prime Video and Crunchyroll beginning with episode 2 on July 2nd.</i>\",\"averageScore\":66,\"popularity\":4869,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784131200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"dN7LV-oVFBg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dN7LV-oVFBg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417397,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784132100,\"media\":{\"id\":184356,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Dogul Wang\",\"english\":\"Tomb Raider King\",\"native\":\"도굴왕\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184356-SlFIstXUXJYP.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184356-SlFIstXUXJYP.png\",\"color\":\"#5d93e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Chaos ensues overnight when mysterious tombs suddenly surface, filled with divine relics granting overwhelming power, triggering a global power struggle to claim them for dominion. Among the havoc, a raider, Jooheon Suh, is betrayed and left for dead until a second chance brings him back years before the relics. Fueled by fury and future knowledge, he sets out to raid each tomb before they arise.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":16589,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784132100},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"6f702O_nnq8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6f702O_nnq8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":412117,\"episode\":17,\"airingAt\":1784194200,\"media\":{\"id\":209541,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"PetitCure: Precure Fairies Season 3\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"ぷちきゅあ～Precure Fairies～ シーズン3\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx209541-p9YKR3vE0Fx6.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx209541-p9YKR3vE0Fx6.jpg\",\"color\":\"#d6e4a1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In Season 3, in addition to the familiar Mysterious Amusement Park and Candy Paradise, many new locations—including a lively performance stage—will make their debut!<br><br>\\nFurthermore, joining the ranks of our active heroes like PetitCure Mofurun and PetitCure Pollun, new friends such as PetitCure Purirun and PetitCure Meroron will also be appearing!<br><br>\\nEverything is even cuter when you're with a friend! ♪<br><br>\\nPlease look forward to more heartwarming and humorous stories that will leave you feeling cozy and healed by all the cute PetitCure. ♡<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Official Website)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":229,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":17,\"airingAt\":1784194200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"4anmA68beog\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4anmA68beog/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413302,\"episode\":41,\"airingAt\":1784199600,\"media\":{\"id\":194389,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Koala Enikki\",\"english\":\"Koala's Diary\",\"native\":\"コアラ絵日記\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx194389-DAbj4TOj5GB9.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx194389-DAbj4TOj5GB9.png\",\"color\":\"#e47843\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The manga is about Koala who writes about daily life, whether it's good or bad, happy or sad, Koala treats every day as a precious day. Koala believes that today is a good day, and tomorrow will be a good day too.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"averageScore\":51,\"popularity\":514,\"episodes\":49,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":41,\"airingAt\":1784199600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"jnSt-yJxigA\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jnSt-yJxigA/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414975,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784205000,\"media\":{\"id\":203880,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Reiwa no Dara-san\",\"english\":\"Dara-san of the Reiwa Era\",\"native\":\"令和のダラさん\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203880-lnruKftb27Nr.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203880-lnruKftb27Nr.png\",\"color\":null},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Clouds blacken the sky and sheets of rain turn the mountain forest into a treacherous maze... A landslide crushes a razor wire fence, and buries a \\\"NO TRESPASSING\\\" sign... Two young siblings wander into a dark world where they do not belong, and a long, horrid shadow rears up to meet them- Anyway, so that's how we met Dara-san! She might look kinda scary, but just wait until you get to know her!<br><br>\\n\\n\\\"Look, I'm a god of misfortune, okay!? Aren't you kids gonna freak out about my grotesque visage!?\\\"<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"averageScore\":61,\"popularity\":8659,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Horror\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784205000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"AZKlUSu5tQ0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/AZKlUSu5tQ0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415202,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784205600,\"media\":{