 bride of a demon fox, and is resented by her family every day. One day, when Yuzu just couldn't take things anymore, a man appears before her on a bridge. This man is the most beautiful man Yuzu has ever seen... and he's calling her his wife?! <i>\\\"Just be quiet and let me hold you.\\\"</i> The most powerful, \\\"cold-hearted\\\" ayakashi is pouring his heart out for Yuzu?!<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\"averageScore\":69,\"popularity\":11978,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784388600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"1hYWc5MCIPk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1hYWc5MCIPk/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415579,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784388600,\"media\":{\"id\":196223,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Cyborg 009: Nemesis\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"サイボーグ009 ネメシス\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196223-IGxBuIsascyV.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196223-IGxBuIsascyV.jpg\",\"color\":\"#3586ff\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"To commemorate the 61st anniversary of the original manga's debut: a new anime based on Shoutarou Ishinomori's <i>Cyborg 009</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":789,\"episodes\":3,\"duration\":30,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784386800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Da_2mAvLs5E\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Da_2mAvLs5E/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415024,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784390100,\"media\":{\"id\":185692,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kabushiki Gaisha Magi Lumiere 2nd Season\",\"english\":\"Magi