e\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/L4wurjkd0JM/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":411665,\"episode\":25,\"airingAt\":1784417400,\"media\":{\"id\":202957,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Meitantei Precure!\",\"english\":\"Star Detective Precure!\",\"native\":\"名探偵プリキュア！\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#d6ae1a\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/202957-B9U0hNv2Dqap.jpg\",\"description\":\"The 23rd installment of the long-running <i>Precure</i> series.<br>\\n<br>\\nAnna Akechi is a second-year junior high student living in Makoto Mirai Town. On her 14th birthday, she has a chance encounter with a fairy named Pochitan, and a magical pendant caused her to travel back in time from 2027 to 1999! In the Makoto Mirai Town 28 years in the past, Anna meets Mikuru Kobayashi, a girl her age who wants to become a great detective.<br>\\n<br>\\nMeanwhile, people in town are in trouble as their prized possessions are being stolen from under their noses - the cause being a group of Phantom Thieves. To stop them, Anna and Mikuru turn into Precures! Maybe if they solve these mysteries, Anna can find her way back to her own time?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Official Website, translated)\",\"averageScore\":74,\"popularity\":5545,\"episodes\":51,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Mahou Shoujo\",\"Mystery\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":25,\"airingAt\":1784417400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"qjozo1fh7OI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qjozo1fh7OI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415931,\"episode\":39,\"airingAt\":1784419200,\"media\":{\"id\":188388,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\",\"english\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\",\"native\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fec928\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/188388-kCSxLPMY2JkD.jpg\",\"description\":\"<i>GLITCH THE FUTURE.</i><br><br>\\n\\nTomoro Tenma lives in a world where human thoughts and emotions—known as “e-Pulse”—power AI devices called Sapotama. But when Digimon begin materializing from Sapotama and feeding on e-Pulse, society begins to fracture. After Gekkomon appears from his device, Tomoro joins Glowing Dawn, a secret team investigating rogue Digimon and the dark truth of a system both fueled and corrupted by emotion. What new future will be forged by humans and Digimon? <br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll, DIGIMON BEATBREAK Official Site, edited)\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":13846,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":39,\"airingAt\":1784419200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"naNctHU5MQE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/naNctHU5MQE/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":410144,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784421000,\"media\":{\"id\":206523,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Onegai AiPri\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"おねがいアイプリ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206523-2IaJCk4R7i63.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206523-2IaJCk4R7i63.jpg\",\"color\":\"#0035ff\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The latest entry in the <i>Pretty Series</i> franchise and a new chapter in the <i>AiPri</i> series.\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Relations are provisional and will be updated when more info is announced.</i>\",\"averageScore\":54,\"popularity\":729,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Music\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784421000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"j5MgjyhhUBc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/j5MgjyhhUBc/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":408234,\"episode\":51,\"airingAt\":1784426400,\"media\":{\"id\":196613,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Dou Po Cangqiong: Nian Fan 4\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"斗破苍穹 年番4\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196613-20kz65bVsHl7.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196613-20kz65bVsHl7.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4935d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The eighth season of Dou Po Cangqiong.<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Episodes 158 to 209.</i>\",\"averageScore\":74,\"popularity\":792,\"episodes\":52,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":51,\"airingAt\":1784426400},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":408344,\"episode\":399,\"airingAt\":1784426400,\"media\":{\"id\":155723,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Wushen Zhuzai: Da Wei Pian\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"武神主宰 大威篇\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx155723-hM261Imc5yfd.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx155723-hM261Imc5yfd.png\",\"color\":\"#c9f1f1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Wushen Zhuzai</i>.\",\"averageScore\":65,\"popularity\":565,\"episodes\":448,\"duration\":7,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":399,\"airingAt\":1784426400},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417284,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784446200,\"media\":{\"id\":200230,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Let's Go Kaikigumi\",\"english\":\"Let's go KAIKIGUMI\",\"native\":\"レッツゴー怪奇組\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx200230-YuzdgbXSgi38.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx200230-YuzdgbXSgi38.png\",\"color\":\"#e45d43\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The horror comedy manga begins one fateful day when the cowardly (unnamed) protagonist meets Mechako, the leader of the \\\"Kaikigumi\\\" organization which is in charge of the ghosts and supernatural creatures scaring humans. The protagonist somehow takes part in the revival of the Kaikigumi, after which one bizarre (yet not scary) phenomenon after another crops up around him.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: ANN)\",\"averageScore\":54,\"popularity\":4215,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Horror\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784446200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"3DKfmW2aDhY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3DKfmW2aDhY/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":412343,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784448000,\"media\":{\"id\":210031,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku 2nd Season\",\"english\":\"You and I Are Polar Opposites Season 2\",\"native\":\"正反対な君と僕 第2期\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx210031-TppgcHZh46LY.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx210031-TppgcHZh46LY.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fe5093\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/210031-M4bt0rAmWk5Q.jpg\",\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Seihantai na Kimi to Boku</i>.\",\"averageScore\":82,\"popularity\":40552,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784448000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"HW7enBbU_hk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HW7enBbU_hk/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413731,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784449800,\"media\":{\"id\":204060,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tetsunabe no Jan!\",\"english\":\"Iron Wok Jan!\",\"native\":\"鉄鍋のジャン！\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204060-bKhovD8jAlW8.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204060-bKhovD8jAlW8.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1931a\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204060-3y19sqCToRaN.jpg\",\"description\":\"Jan Akiyama, a cocky arrogant teenager wants to fulfill his grandfathers wish of defeating his arch nemesis Mutsuju Gobancho. When he arrives at the Gobancho restaurant he meets his granddaughter Kiriko Gobancho. Their rivalry is easily compared to Jan's and Kiriko's grandfathers, for Jan believes cooking is about competition and Kiriko believes cooking is about heart.\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":6418,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784449800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"awvmDnz3URo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/awvmDnz3URo/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416916,\"episode\":375,\"airingAt\":1784451600,\"media\":{\"id\":118123,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Holo no Graffiti\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"ホロのぐらふぃてぃ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png\",\"color\":\"#e4ae5d\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/118123-BvHyzWd850nZ.jpg\",\"description\":\"From unraveling the secrets of opening and closing doors to defusing surprise packages more commonly known as bombs, there is never a dull day at the Hololive Production office! <i>Holo no Graffiti</i> follows an eccentric cast of Virtual YouTubers, also known as \\\"VTubers,\\\" going about their absurd yet hilarious daily lives, detailing all their cute moments and mishaps.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)\",\"averageScore\":78,\"popularity\":14420,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2019,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":375,\"airingAt\":1784451600},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":394981,\"episode\":2841,\"airingAt\":1784453400,\"media\":{\"id\":2406,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sazae-san\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"サザエさん\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb43\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2406-ROqXxejQ5bH9.jpg\",\"description\":\"The main character is a mother named Sazae-san. She lives in a house with her husband, her kid, her siblings and her parents. The show is the ultimate family program and tends to follow traditional themes. Think of this show as the Japanese equivalent to \\\"The Partridge Family\\\" and you'll get a good feel for this show's atmosphere. Don't expect to see things like violence, swearing, kung-fu action or magical girls. The plots are more like \\\"Today, Sazae-san goes to the new mall and gets lost\\\". Such \\\"boring\\\" plotlines and the simplistic art are often a turn-off to non-Japanese audiences, but most Japanese find the show incredibly good. As a result, it continues to be one of the top ratings grabbers on TV and is one of the few anime that is considered \\\"acceptable\\\" by adults.\",\"averageScore\":55,\"popularity\":2459,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":1969,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2841,\"airingAt\":1784453400},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413669,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784466000,\"media\":{\"id\":198409,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sekai Saikyou no Kouei: Meikyuukoku no Shinjin Tansakusha\",\"english\":\"The World's Strongest Rearguard\",\"native\":\"世界最強の後衛 ～迷宮国の新人探索者～\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198409-EiWJXfYnvfu4.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198409-EiWJXfYnvfu4.png\",\"color\":\"#0dbbfe\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"After a fatal accident, overworked office worker Arihito Atobe is reborn in the Labyrinth Country as a Seeker with the rare Rearguard class—an all-purpose support role that excels in attack, defense, and healing. Joined by a fierce demi-human mercenary and his former boss, Arihito dives into deadly dungeons and rises through the ranks. The adventure of the strongest support class begins!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":59,\"popularity\":17962,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784466000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"vdJo_3uZ92s\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.y