f Wang Lin, an ordinary young man in the countryside, who is moved by his heart and cultivates against immortality. His pursuit is not only for longevity, but also for getting rid of the ants behind it. He firmly believed in human beings and entered the path of cultivation with mediocre qualifications. After experiencing ups and downs, with his wise mind, he gradually reached the pinnacle and became famous in the cultivation world with his own strength.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: WeTV)\",\"averageScore\":82,\"popularity\":5550,\"episodes\":180,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":150,\"airingAt\":1784512800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"2rj8eXmgR3Y\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2rj8eXmgR3Y/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415476,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784548620,\"media\":{\"id\":169582,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Saikyou Degarashi Ouji no Anyaku Teii Arasoi: Munou wo Enjiru SS Rank Ouji wa Koui Keishou-sen wo Kage kara Shihai suru\",\"english\":\"The Insipid Prince's Furtive Grab for the Throne\",\"native\":\"最強出涸らし皇子の暗躍帝位争い 無能を演じるSSランク皇子は皇位継承戦を影から支配する\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx169582-quL8VMg45fcu.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx169582-quL8VMg45fcu.png\",\"color\":\"#f1e4c9\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"To the empire, Prince Arnold is one big joke, a completely inept prince outshone by his more talented twin, Leonard. But in secret, Arnold operates as Silver, one of only five magic-wielding SS-rank adventurers on the continent. As the bloody battle for the throne intensifies after the crown prince’s death, Arnold pulls the strings from the shadows to crown his twin emperor to his own advantage.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":64,\"popularity\":15386,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784548620},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"tcaxQBQMTEk\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/tcaxQBQMTEk/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414576,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784548800,\"media\":{\"id\":202269,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Toumei na Yoru ni Kakeru Kimi to, Me ni Mienai Koi wo Shita.\",\"english\":\"Love Unseen Beneath the Clear Night Sky\",\"native\":\"透明な夜に駆ける君と、目に見えない恋をした。\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202269-7KNj8s2fSsJJ.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202269-7KNj8s2fSsJJ.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"On an April night in Tokyo, still too early for fireworks, university student Kakeru Sorano meets a woman named Koharu Fuyutsuki. She is a beautiful girl who stands out from the crowd, laughs a lot, and exudes a warmth that contrasts sharply with Kakeru's own introversion. But there was something Kakeru didn't know at first—she can't see.<br>\\n<br>\\nUnlike Kakeru, Koharu hasn't given up on anything, even with her blindness. She attends university daily, shows interest in clubs, makes friends—and dreams of launching fireworks one day. Kakeru wonders why, when she can't see them...but maybe it doesn't matter. And maybe he can start moving forward, too, for the girl who's always been by his side<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"averageScore\":76,\"popularity\":23693,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784548800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OPZ7TOGxWqI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OPZ7TOGxWqI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414504,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784552400,\"media\":{\"id\":185542,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Gaikotsu Kishi-sama, Tadaima Isekai e Odekakechuu II\",\"english\":\"Skeleton Knight in Another World Season 2\",\"native\":\"骸骨騎士様、只今異世界へお出掛け中Ⅱ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185542-6a9LCWlLHa0T.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185542-6a9LCWlLHa0T.jpg\",\"color\":\"#286bbb\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Gaikotsu Kishi-sama, Tadaima Isekai e Odekakechuu</i>.\",\"averageScore\":69,\"popularity\":35406,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784552400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Enu3fyOdkoM\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Enu3fyOdkoM/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415545,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784552400,\"media\":{\"id\":206521,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"World Is Dancing\",\"english\":\"The World Is Dancing\",\"native\":\"ワールド イズ ダンシング\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206521-ecJuDgjth84C.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206521-ecJuDgjth84C.png\",\"color\":\"#e45d78\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/206521-zCIAGsiIkh6G.jpg\",\"description\":\"Born into a life of acting and dance with a traveling theater troupe in 14th-century Japan, 12-year old Oniyasha has one problem—he doesn't know what the point of any of it is. \\\"Why must I step with the left foot here instead of the right? Why is one performance good and another, bad? Why do people dance at all?\\\" It all seems perfectly arbitrary, until a chance encounter in a run-down shack sets him down a path to revolutionizing the art form and influencing much of Japanese culture to come. A fictionalized account of the early life of Zeami Motokiyo (Oniyasha), the founder of modern Noh theater—the world's oldest surviving theater art—this coming-of-age artist's journey vividly brings to life a man far ahead of his time during one of Japan's most culturally and socially vibrant eras.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Kodansha Comics)<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: World Is Dancing is streaming 3 days in advance of the TV broadcast on Prime Video and HIDIVE beginning June 29th, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 2nd, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":73,\"popularity\":16946,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784552400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"h2zytdkjAU8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/h2zytdkjAU8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415036,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784554200,\"media\":{\"id\":199408,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Buchigire Reijou wa Houfuku wo Chikaimashita.: Madousho no Chikara de Sokoku wo Tataki Tsubushimasu\",\"english\":\"A Livid Lady’s Guide to Getting Even: How I Crushed My Homeland with My Mighty Grimoires\",\"native\":\"ブチ切れ令嬢は報復を誓いました。　～魔導書の力で祖国を叩き潰します～\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199408-ocRWG4pRWl8f.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199408-ocRWG4pRWl8f.png\",\"color\":\"#f1ae35\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/199408-ouNGkjrw0ohT.jpg\",\"description\":\"Elizabeth Leiston, daughter of the influential prime minister, is a picture-perfect lady on the path to becoming the future queen of the Kingdom of Haldoria. But her life takes a sudden turn for the worst when her fiancé makes a show of publicly calling off their engagement. Soon after, he throws her in jail and starts spreading nasty rumors about her. The encouragement Elizabeth receives from her loyal waiting maid, Mireille, and her inner fury are all she needs to reconsider her goals. Why should she continue devoting herself to a country that doesn’t respect her when she can trample over it instead? She will get even with those who wronged her and bring down the damned kingdom, even if it’s the last thing she does! Luckily, Elizabeth is no damsel in distress and has seven powerful magic grimoires she won’t hesitate to use. Get ready because this ruthless lady is out for blood!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"averageScore\":69,\"popularity\":12993,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784554200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"yC4TghEG8q8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/yC4TghEG8q8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414478,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784556000,\"media\":{\"id\":195833,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honoo no Toukyuujyo Dodge Danko\",\"english\":\"Flaming Dodgeball Girl Danko\",\"native\":\"炎の闘球女 ドッジ弾子\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx195833-h7x6i3NQWROA.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx195833-h7x6i3NQWROA.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1860d\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/195833-DlR4ToMXP3if.jpg\",\"description\":\"The sequel to the legendary dodgeball manga <i>Honou no Toukyuuji Dodge Danpei</i>! In this modern version of the hot-blooded dodgeball story, Danpei's daughter, Danko, follows in his footsteps, struggling to build a dodgeball team with the strongest fighting spirit in the modern age of 2025! Can Danko overcome the apathetic attitude of today's world? \\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Corocoro, translated)\",\"averageScore\":55,\"popularity\":1297,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Sports\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784556000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"IRbt0J3l5js\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IRbt0J3l5js/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415153,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784556000,\"media\":{\"id\":209504,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Suterare Seijo no Isekai Gohantabi: Kakure Skill de Camping Car wo Shoukan Shimashita\",\"english\":\"The Forsaken Saintess and Her Foodie Roadtrip in Another World\",\"native\":\"捨てられ聖女の異世界ごはん旅 隠れスキルでキャンピングカーを召喚しました\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx209504-yRxHWxKuNGtg.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx209504-yRxHWxKuNGtg.jpg\",\"color\":\"#bbe40d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Rin Takanashi, a caregiver in her thirties, was unceremoniously discarded as \\\"trash\\\" despite being summoned as a saint.\\n<br><br>\\nHowever, as a lover of the great outdoors and all things camping, she was blessed with a special skill, \\\"Survival,\\\" as well as another unique skill! Thus, a riveting tale begins: one of sweat, tears, and insatiable hunger as Rin, together with companions she picked up along the way, leisurely explores this parallel world and savours gourmet cuisine to her heart's content...\\n<br><br>\\nOr so the story should have gone, but it looks like their road is going in an unexpected direction...?\",\"averageScore\":62,\"popularity\":8851,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784556000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"VS0bW7JnEm0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VS0bW7JnEm0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415532,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784557800,\"media\":{\"id\":169583,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tenkousaki no Seiso Karen na Bishoujo ga, Mukashi Danshi to Omotte Issho ni Asonda Osananajimi datta Ken\",\"english\":\"Oh Boy, Was I Wrong About Her\",\"native\":\"転校先の清楚可憐な美少女が、昔男子と思って一緒に遊んだ幼馴染だった件\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx169583-0ZTdBGrKNIbe.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx169583-0ZTdBGrKNIbe.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50c9fe\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Seven years after making a childhood promise to always be friends, Hayato is reunited with his formerly tomboyish pal Haruki at a city high school–only now, Haruki has transformed into the girl every guy dreams about! While Haruki’s looks may have changed, with Hayato, she’s still the same pal he remembers. Despite years apart, their promise and feelings remain and deepen into something stronger.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":70,\"popularity\":21662,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784557800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"UTsFnJgDJz8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UTsFnJgDJz8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":412621,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784559600,\"media\":{\"id\":197754,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"english\":\"LIAR GAME\",\"native\":\"LIAR GAME\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx197754-Q5KqcUhIdypp.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx197754-Q5KqcUhIdypp.png\",\"color\":null},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/197754-cMWxeRdhYrFW.jpg\",\"description\":\"Wishing she would live up to the ideal, Kanzaki Nao's father named her thusly for “honesty”. Nao has more than lived up to her father's wishes--even exceeding them and earning the label of \\\"a foolishly honest girl\\\". This makes Nao the least qualified candidate for the high stakes 'Liar Game', where winning requires deceiving the opponent out of their money and losing means receiving massive debt. However, that doesn't stop a box containing a hundred million yen in cash and a card informing her of her participation in the game from arriving at her doorstep, nor does it stop her from being promptly tricked out of the entire sum of money. Upon hearing that a genius swindler, responsible for the bankruptcy of a major corporation, is being released from jail, Nao goes to the swindler, Shinichi Akiyama, to enlist his help. With that, the two are drawn into the dark, greed-filled, and deceptive world of the Liar Game.\",\"averageScore\":61,\"popularity\":38249,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Psychological\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784559600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"FIPOXj00ysQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/FIPOXj00ysQ/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415141,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784559600,\"media\":{\"id\":199111,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Grand Blue Season 3\",\"english\":\"Grand Blue Dreaming Season 3\",\"native\":\"ぐらんぶる Season 3\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199111-gBSuBG61ElcW.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199111-gBSuBG61ElcW.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daed6\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/199111-Z8y9awn2Zb6v.jpg\",\"description\":\"The third season of <i>Grand Blue</i>.\",\"averageScore\":82,\"popularity\":30770,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\",\"Sports\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784559600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"KJw6ZZaMOWA\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KJw6ZZaMOWA/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413041,\"episode\":362,\"airingAt\":1784587200,\"media\":{\"id\":140842,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chiikawa\",\"english\":\"Chiikawa\",\"native\":\"ちいかわ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx140842-T0geOCa3zS0A.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx140842-T0geOCa3zS0A.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4d6ae\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/140842-kXw5xtsCy8QT.jpg\",\"description\":\"The sometimes happy, sometimes sad, and a tad stressful daily life of \\\"some sort of small, cute creature\\\" known as Chiikawa. Chiikawa enjoys delicious food with bees and rabbits, toils hard every day for the rewards of work, and still maintains a smile.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\\n\",\"averageScore\":84,\"popularity\":9720,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2022,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":361,\"airingAt\":1784241600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"m4yfCS_YBUU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/m4yfCS_YBUU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}}]}]]}]\n","segmentData":{"/_tree":":HL[\"/_next/static/css/48ac9a264001a396.css\",\"style\"]\n:HL[\"/_next/static/css/0144fc6fd07b6a6f.css\",\"style\"]\n0:{\"tree\":{\"name\":\"\