"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784644200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"OKEoQo3cGVg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/OKEoQo3cGVg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414661,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784041200,\"media\":{\"id\":198709,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tefuda ga Oome no Victoria\",\"english\":\"Victoria of Many Faces\",\"native\":\"手札が多めのビクトリア\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198709-3PFLvU6eqPvf.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198709-3PFLvU6eqPvf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5da1e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In an age when spies act behind the scenes in every land, Chloe spends her days successfully carrying out even the most difficult missions due to her unparalleled disguise skills and martial arts abilities. After the betrayal of her boss, she suddenly disappears—as Chloe plans to redo her life as the ordinary citizen Victoria in the neighboring kingdom of Ashberry, striving for a “normal” life. However, Victoria's peaceful life is abruptly cut short as she begins to get involved with many people. In this new land, her experiences and abilities from her days as a spy come in far more useful than she ever expected! On the other hand, the second prince--and others--take an interest in Victoria's strength, and the shadows close in on the woman with many faces…\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Yen Press)\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":9188,\"episodes\":9,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784646000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"dm8QPSlRYdI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dm8QPSlRYdI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414242,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784046900,\"media\":{\"id\":207809,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Sora wa Akai Kawa no Hotori\",\"english\":\"Red River\",\"native\":\"天は赤い河のほとり\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207809-cpS7CAyjN7iP.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207809-cpS7CAyjN7iP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4bb5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"After a mysterious hand drags her beneath a puddle, modern Japanese teenager Yuri awakens in the Hittite Empire of the 14th century BCE. Thrust into a deadly struggle for the throne, she joins Prince Kail to battle assassins, outwit royal conspiracies, and survive a world at war. As her exploits earn her renown as the goddess Ishtar, Yuri must choose between her old life and an uncertain future.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":61,\"popularity\":7753,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784651700},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"qpFcQ1Bek08\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qpFcQ1Bek08/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416107,\"episode\":28,\"airingAt\":1784070000,\"media\":{\"id\":204656,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"mofusand\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"mofusand\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b204656-KXjxVB4bBhl8.jpg\",\"color\":\"#c9e443\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204656-ECYkRJKBxTLj.jpg\",\"description\":\"Shark Meow is an orange tabby kitty who wears a shark suit.<br>\\nA little clumsy and always taking things at their own cozy pace,<br>\\nbut every day with their best kitty friends — and the rescued baby kitty, Little Meow —<br>\\nis filled with unexpected little mishaps and sweet adventures.<br><br>\\n \\nA sunny warm spot in the park, the sparkle of the sea,<br>\\nsteam rising from freshly roasted sweet potatoes,<br>\\nthe fluttery feeling of the first snowfall…<br>\\nThese small everyday moments fill their world with warmth and delight.\\n <br><br>\\nYou can’t help but smile and think, “So true!”<br>\\nA soft and snuggly kitty anime that brings joy to everyday moments.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: QTORY Channel)\",\"averageScore\":60,\"popularity\":789,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":1,\"genres\":[\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":28,\"airingAt\":1784070000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Svh_xgdMWlU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Svh_xgdMWlU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415999,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784077200,\"media\":{\"id\":212309,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Transformers: Wild King W\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"トランスフォーマー ワイルドキングW\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx212309-gDqt6qz1RPEL.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx212309-gDqt6qz1RPEL.png\",\"color\":\"#3593e4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"A sequel to <i>Transformers: Wild King</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":117,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":4,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Mecha\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784077200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"6gyPgg1YdYg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6gyPgg1YdYg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415493,\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1784080800,\"media\":{\"id\":213297,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yun Shen Buzhi Meng Special: Zhu Ming Zhi Yi\",\"english\":\"Eclipse of Illusion SP: The Miasma War\",\"native\":\"云深不知梦 特别篇：逐冥之役\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213297-hmYPfAXgQQDp.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213297-hmYPfAXgQQDp.jpg\",\"color\":\"#bbd6f1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In the primordial apocalypse, Xihe, a maiden of the Huihua Clan, fled the brutal rebellion in her ancestral homeland. Breaking free from the control of the Qiongming Demon Tribe, she embarks on a quest for the Demonslayer Divine Sword, igniting the War of the Six Armies.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":97,\"episodes\":6,\"duration\":22,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":6,\"airingAt\":1784080800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416941,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784084400,\"media\":{\"id\":213703,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Jiaonang Jihua: Qiji\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"胶囊计划 奇迹\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213703-ghO1AqW0bdaN.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213703-ghO1AqW0bdaN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb0d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"\\\"Capsules Project\\\" is a collection of domestically produced animated short films created by a professional team with mature animation production experience. With the creative theme of \\\"extreme emotion + independent theme,\\\" it does not restrict the creative form, exploring the possibilities of animation together with the team. The aim is to collaboratively create original short films with diverse styles and characteristics, and to help Chinese animators reach the world stage. \\\"Miracle\\\" represents transcending conventions and breaking through limitations to achieve extraordinary success, often accompanied by a sense of mystery that inspires awe and curiosity. What miracles will occur in these 10 stories?\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":41,\"episodes\":8,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784084400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"XvuUOmNUtxc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XvuUOmNUtxc/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415968,\"episode\":10,\"airingAt\":1784103300,\"media\":{\"id\":163793,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Cheongchun Blossom: Uriui Bom\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"청춘블라썸 : 우리의 봄\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163793-dOI9QEcIrgBS.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163793-dOI9QEcIrgBS.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45d93\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Oh, to be young and in love. Oh, to be wild and carefree. The springtime of life is intense, tumultuous, and at times, oh so confusing. Spring, summer, fall and winter -- love blossoms in all seasons.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: WEBTOON)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":3625,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":15,\"genres\":[\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":10,\"airingAt\":1784103300},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413528,\"episode\":40,\"airingAt\":1784113200,\"media\":{\"id\":188529,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ugoku! Neko Mukashi Banashi\",\"english\":\"Cat Tales\",\"native\":\"うごく！ねこむかしばなし\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188529-6o9byjahRpEx.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e46b5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"What if cats appeared in that story…? When beloved old tales and fairy stories are joined by cats, a surreal and heartwarming new adventure begins…!? Tabby cats, orange cats, calico cats, and white cats— a delightful mix of feline friends woven into timeless stories is sure to soothe the hearts of all humanity! A charming cat comedy is about to unfold!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: AniOne Asia)\",\"averageScore\":52,\"popularity\":541,\"episodes\":50,\"duration\":3,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":40,\"airingAt\":1784113200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"n-jg8syMe08\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/n-jg8syMe08/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417384,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784116800,\"media\":{\"id\":198946,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Clevatess II: Majuu no Ou to Itsuwari no Yuusha Denshou\",\"english\":\"Clevatess Season 2\",\"native\":\"クレバテスⅡ-魔獣の王と偽りの勇者伝承-\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198946-IGXmbqBEYRYD.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198946-IGXmbqBEYRYD.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb5d\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Clevatess: Majuu no Ou to Akago to Kabane no Yuusha</i>.\",\"averageScore\":75,\"popularity\":30646,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784116800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"0N1-8XY_3Rs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/0N1-8XY_3Rs/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414761,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784118600,\"media\":{\"id\":135865,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Youjo Senki II\",\"english\":\"Saga of Tanya the Evil Season 2\",\"native\":\"幼女戦記Ⅱ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx135865-T7XIPMAbqcxN.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx135865-T7XIPMAbqcxN.png\",\"color\":\"#e46b28\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Youjo Senki</i>.\",\"averageScore\":81,\"popularity\":76202,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784118600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"kUvhvkPDvm0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kUvhvkPDvm0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417451,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784120400,\"media\":{\"id\":213666,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Perfect Addiction\",\"english\":\"Perfect Addiction\",\"native\":\"パーフェクトアディクション\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213666-nnKcumRblZi1.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213666-nnKcumRblZi1.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4bba1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Akihito is a college student obsessed with looks and sex, but he can't stand the handsome-yet-aloof Sae. Things come to a head when Akihito is shot down at a singles mixer by a girl who's set her romantic sights on Sae. Furious, he follows Sae to the hotel district where he learns Sae's secret: he's gay, and a bottom. Sae confesses he's been having trouble feeling pleasure from sex. Breaking through Sae's mental barriers is exactly the lovemaking challenge Akihito needed. It awakens something in them both. Will they ever be able to control themselves again?<br><br>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":1199,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":5,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASIN