600,\"media\":{\"id\":197715,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"LV999 no Murabito\",\"english\":\"The Villager of Level 999\",\"native\":\"LV999の村人\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx197715-KLFLxU24U1uL.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx197715-KLFLxU24U1uL.png\",\"color\":\"#5daef1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"In Earthclear, everyone is born into a fixed role, and villagers are the weakest of all. Most never rise above Level 5—except Kouji Kagami, who is Level…999?! On a monster hunt, he meets Alice, the Demon King’s daughter, and discovers they share an impossible dream: coexistence between humans and demons. In a world destined for conflict, they charge into battle to defy fate and shatter the rules.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":64,\"popularity\":25580,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784127600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"YfWJLXcN7hI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YfWJLXcN7hI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417410,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784127600,\"media\":{\"id\":213961,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Youjo Shenki 2\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"ようじょしぇんき2\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b213961-x2ZvvtkYSTC9.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b213961-x2ZvvtkYSTC9.png\",\"color\":\"#f1d693\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Youjo Shenki</i>.<br><br>\\n\\nChibi parody of Youjo Senki.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":444,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"