\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":2230,\"episodes\":52,\"duration\":1,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Music\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":41,\"airingAt\":1784206800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"7WsRmVZspYI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7WsRmVZspYI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417139,\"episode\":5,\"airingAt\":1784210400,\"media\":{\"id\":198376,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"BanG Dream! Yume∞Mita\",\"english\":\"BanG Dream! YUME∞MITA\",\"native\":\"バンドリ！ ゆめ∞みた\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198376-sc5qcFv0RSH9.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198376-sc5qcFv0RSH9.jpg\",\"color\":\"#a1f150\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198376-1b4DxjIUwMIY.jpg\",\"description\":\"Suddenly thrown together, a group of girls are now debuting as the virtual band, Mugendai Mewtype. They’ve got talent and personality, but no clue how to perform as one. Can they survive, let alone make it to the top in this unforgiving music world?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":72,\"popularity\":5290,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Music\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":5,\"airingAt\":1784210400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"sMcHl3g6aS4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sMcHl3g6aS4/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414587,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784212200,\"media\":{\"id\":108992,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mebius Dust\",\"english\":\"Mebius Dust\",\"native\":\"メビウス・ダスト\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx108992-skuOsfmLmMd2.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx108992-skuOsfmLmMd2.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50bbc9\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"On February 29, 2000, a group of Möbius meteorites fell down to earth. These meteorites brought new material called Möbius Dust, which dissolves in air and can cause miracles. The day the Möbius meteorites fell was dubbed 2.29, and the economic disparity in Japan increased dramatically after that day. A group of people fed up with the wealth inequality fought back with acts of terrorism. The police established a special group to fight against the terrorists and a school to train members for that group.\\n<br></br>\\n(Sources: Comic Natalie, Live Chart)\",\"averageScore\":53,\"popularity\":6651,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784212200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ByOF3FLlAws\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ByOF3FLlAws/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415164,\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784213760,\"media\":{\"id\":196187,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Super no Ura de Yani Suu Futari\",\"english\":\"Smoking Behind the Supermarket with You\",\"native\":\"スーパーの裏でヤニ吸うふたり\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196187-0dgFi2CPp3xn.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196187-0dgFi2CPp3xn.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1c9bb\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196187-Z9dV6uotmKjM.jpg\",\"description\":\"At age forty-five, office worker Sasaki has had enough of the corporate grind. His only solace is smoking-and the friendly smile of supermarket cashier Yamada. When Sasaki can't find Yamada after a particularly trying day, a striking woman invites him to smoke with her. The despondent man thinks he's made a new smoking buddy in the cool, teasing Tayama, but Sasaki doesn't realize he already knows her!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Square Enix)<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: Episodes 1-6 had an early release by ABEMA and Crunchyroll on June 3rd, 2026 in a mini-episode batch format that splits 6 episodes into 12, ahead of the TV broadcast which started on July 9th, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":83,\"popularity\":85823,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":2,\"airingAt\":1784213760},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"aOOwNK6Ul6E\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aOOwNK6Ul6E/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":408482,\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784214000,\"media\":{\"id\":206819,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kimi to Hanabi to Yakusoku to\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"君と花火と約束と\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206819-9VJOdSC6yFET.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206819-9VJOdSC6yFET.jpg\",\"color\":\"#d6a178\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/206819-4oLkAimSr18r.jpg\",\"description\":\"The story centers on two Tokyo high schoolers who connect over a painting of fireworks. They trace the painting to the Nagaoka Fireworks Festival in Niigata, one of Japan's three major fireworks festivals, and to a mysterious promise that connects the two to the past.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News, edited) \\n\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":4549,\"episodes\":1,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"MOVIE\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784214000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"zwiemWqog74\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zwiemWqog74/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414952,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784214000,\"media\":{\"id\":208044,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Rakudai Kenja no Gakuin Musou: Nidome no Tensei, S-Rank Cheat Majutsushi Bouken-roku\",\"english\":\"From Overshadowed to Overpowered: Second Reincarnation of a Talentless Sage\",\"native\":\"落第賢者の学院無双～二度目の転生、Sランクチート魔術師冒険録～\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx208044-Pm2UhvApQFUh.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx208044-Pm2UhvApQFUh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1d61a\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Ephtal is reincarnated as a human, coming from modern Earth. In this new world where magic is real, he decides to devote the entirety of his life in the pursuit of magic. Despite his efforts, though, he discovers that he is absolutely talentless in magic, and breathed his last in anguish....But it isn't the end for him just yet! He reincarnates once again bearing the same name, Ephtal, 400 years later. Having retained his knowledge and power, he steals his resolve and once again sets his sights for the peak of magic!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Comikey)<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: Rakudai Kenja no Gakuin Musou: Nidome no Tensei, S-Rank Cheat Majutsushi Bouken-roku is streaming a week in advance of the TV broadcast on dAnimeStore, ABEMA, U-NEXT, and Anime Hodai beginning June 26th, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 2nd, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":66,\"popularity\":30391,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784214000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"QOeItd-RrVs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QOeItd-RrVs/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416988,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784215560,\"media\":{\"id\":180136,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tsuihou Sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou Suru\",\"english\":\"The Exiled Heavy Knight Knows How to Game the System\",\"native\":\"追放された転生重騎士はゲーム知識で無双する\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx180136-gtMTCRlOD4OE.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx180136-gtMTCRlOD4OE.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50c9fe\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Born into a prestigious family of master swordsmen, Elymas Edvaughn’s future shatters when he awakens the so-called “defective” Heavy Knight class. Disowned and cast out, he regains memories of another life—and realizes this world mirrors a VR game he once mastered. Armed with knowledge no one else possesses, he sets out to rewrite his fate and prove the strength of the “weakest” class.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":37669,\"episodes\":26,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784215560},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"uC13b3_8riU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uC13b3_8riU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":412632,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784215800,\"media\":{\"id\":207141,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yani Neko\",\"english\":\"Chainsmoker Cat\",\"native\":\"ヤニねこ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207141-h5q5KJPd6vaX.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207141-h5q5KJPd6vaX.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50a1f1\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207141-MvHAS2YVfJzL.jpg\",\"description\":\"Yani is a catgirl with a seriously bad smoking habit. She smokes so much that her apartment smells like ash and is littered with cigarette butts—and plenty of other trash! Every time she tries to quit, she becomes weak to the cravings and gives in almost instantly. Will she ever get her life together, or is she doomed to live as a chainsmoking slob forever? \\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":43515,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784215800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"KYGgyQtSAdI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KYGgyQtSAdI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414963,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784219280,\"media\":{\"id\":204466,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Otome Kaijuu Caramelise\",\"english\":\"KAIJU GIRL CARAMELISE\",\"native\":\"乙女怪獣キャラメリゼ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx204466-vXMvIs4VOoQd.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx204466-vXMvIs4VOoQd.png\",\"color\":\"#e45d78\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/204466-cpbNGN9qHrGP.jpg\",\"description\":\"Kuroe Akaishi just wants a normal high school life—but that’s impossible with a rare condition that turns her into a giant kaiju whenever her emotions spike! Things get even worse when she falls for Arata Minami, the most popular boy in class. Now every blush, heartbeat, and crush could trigger a monster transformation. Can Kuroe survive high school love before it destroys everything around her?!<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":75,\"popularity\":24247,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784219280},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ECtHlHde3EQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ECtHlHde3EQ/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":363050,\"episode\":665,\"airingAt\":1784239800,\"media\":{\"id\":8336,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hanakappa\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"はなかっぱ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8336-BJzIHFC49RWb.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8336-BJzIHFC49RWb.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1ae43\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Story about Kappa with flowers on their heads.\",\"averageScore\":47,\"popularity\":390,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":10,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2010,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":665,\"airingAt\":1784239800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413040,\"episode\":361,\"airingAt\":1784241600,\"media\":{\"id\":140842,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Chiikawa\",\"english\":\"Chiikawa\",\"native\":\"ちいかわ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx140842-T0geOCa3zS0A.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx140842-T0geOCa3zS0A.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4d6ae\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/140842-kXw5xtsCy8QT.jpg\",\"description\":\"The sometimes happy, sometimes sad, and a tad stressful daily life of \\\"some sort of small, cute creature\\\" known as Chiikawa. Chiikawa enjoys delicious food with bees and rabbits, toils hard every day for the rewards of work, and still maintains a smile.<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\\n\",\"averageScore\":84,\"popularity\":9720,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2022,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":361,\"airingAt\":1784241600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"m4yfCS_YBUU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/m4yfCS_YBUU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416638,\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1784260800,\"media\":{\"id\":213484,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Bai Ri Cheng Wang\",\"english\":\"Crowned in a Hundred Days\",\"native\":\"百日成王\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213484-FIyYH43ASHgB.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213484-FIyYH43ASHgB.png\",\"color\":\"#1a86f1\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/213484-Apezw4iSrrr6.jpg\",\"description\":\"Driven to the brink of despair, restaurant owner Ming forms an unlikely bond with the soul of the true King Lie after swallowing it to save his loved one. Bound together by fate, the two embark on a perilous journey to challenge the tyrant who has usurped the throne.<br><br>\\nWith only one hundred days to change their destiny, Ming uses his extraordinary memory to master long-lost magic, gathering allies and winning the support of the people along the way. As their strength grows, so does their resolve to overthrow a corrupt regime, reclaim the rightful king's throne, and restore peace to the realm.<br><br>\\n(Source: Bilibili TV)\",\"averageScore\":60,\"popularity\":1629,\"episodes\":25,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":8,\"airingAt\":1784260800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"IYcGvpXYfGE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IYcGvpXYfGE/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417205,\"episode\":143,\"airingAt\":1784282100,\"media\":{\"id\":158871,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Pocket Monsters (2023)\",\"english\":\"Pokémon Horizons: The Series\",\"native\":\"ポケットモンスター (2023)\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx158871-GBM9AMDfDRSu.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx158871-GBM9AMDfDRSu.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4bb28\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/158871-jKfsW5HCGA3K.jpg\",\"description\":\"A new dream and adventure set throughout the entire Pokémon world unfolds in a brand new Pokémon-series following a girl named Liko and a boy named Roy.\",\"averageScore\":73,\"popularity\":23621,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2023,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":143,\"airingAt\":1784282100},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"_c_hMehCORQ\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_c_hMehCORQ/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417261,\"episode\":130,\"airingAt\":1784282400,\"media\":{\"id\":165159,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"BEYBLADE X\",\"english\":\"BEYBLADE X\",\"native\":\"BEYBLADE X\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx165159-aCFC9Sng7t4M.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx165159-aCFC9Sng7t4M.png\",\"color\":\"#28aee4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Bird Kazami, aiming to become a pro Blader, meets former champion Ekusu Kurosu, also known as 'Kamen X', and forms a team so that they can aim for the \\\"top\\\" of the X Tower. But what awaits them is a spectacular battle that no one has ever seen before. The yet unseen 'X'. The super accelerated (Xtreme) Beyblade runs through a new era!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Official website)\",\"averageScore\":64,\"popularity\":4370,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":22,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Sports\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2023,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":130,\"airingAt\":1784282400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"SXdTmFshlFs\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SXdTmFshlFs/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415428,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784295000,\"media\":{\"id\":199748,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Koko wa Ore ni Makasete Saki ni Ike to Ittekara 10-nen ga Tattara Densetsu ni Natteita.\",\"english\":\"I Became a Legend After My 10 Year-Long Last Stand\",\"native\":\"ここは俺に任せて先に行けと言ってから１０年がたったら伝説になっていた。\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199748-PAFk9pGSUmFL.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199748-PAFk9pGSUmFL.png\",\"color\":\"#5dd6f1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Luck, an S-rank mage in the hero’s party, makes a last stand against the Demon King to save his companions. When he finally returns victorious, ten years have passed, and the world praises him as a legendary hero who died in battle. Unable to reclaim his former life, Luck conceals his identity and begins again as “Lock,” an F-rank adventurer forging a future in a world that moved on without him.<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\\n<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: Koko wa Ore ni Makasete Saki ni Ike to Ittekara 10-nen ga Tattara Densetsu ni Natteita is streaming 3 days in advance of the TV broadcast on Prime Video beginning July 3rd, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 6th, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":66,\"popularity\":25624,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784295000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"_9FRdFYJOdg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_9FRdFYJOdg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415652,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784295000,\"media\":{\"id\":196218,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ryoumin 0-Nin Start no Henkyou Ryoushu-sama\",\"english\":\"The Frontier Lord Begins with Zero Subjects\",\"native\":\"領民0人スタートの辺境領主様\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196218-UsdTTCrwpDIN.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196218-UsdTTCrwpDIN.jpg\",\"color\":\"#febb50\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196218-lX0y9T76KQkC.jpg\",\"description\":\"Dias finally returns home after decades of war. He's hailed as a hero and promptly rewarded with his own domain...which turns out to be little more than empty plains. Population: zero. Dias, who has only ever known battle, finds himself at a loss. How is he supposed to survive, let alone cultivate his territory into a thriving, prosperous dominion when there's nothing but grass as far as can see? \\n<br><br>\\nFortunately for Dias, a horned girl by the name of Alna is about to show him there's more to the plains than meets the eye! \\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)<br><br>\\n\\n<i>Note: Ryoumin 0-Nin Start no Henkyou Ryoushu-sama is streaming a week advance of the TV broadcast on Prime Video beginning July 3rd, 2026. Regular broadcasting began on July 10th, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":19783,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\",\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784295000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"5JpTU6wj_-g\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5JpTU6wj_-g/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413370,\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784296800,\"media\":{\"id\":182205,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 4th Season\",\"english\":\"That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime Season 4\",\"native\":\"転生したらスライムだった件 第4期\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182205-q2AeO1owuQbO.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182205-q2AeO1owuQbO.jpg\",\"color\":\"#1abbd6\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182205-fRUoKv6f2JAq.jpg\",\"description\":\"The fourth season of <i>Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken</i>.<br><br>\\nDemon Lord Rimuru's dream of creating an alliance between humans and monsters takes a step closer to being realized. As Tempest continues to prosper, Granville Rozzo and his granddaughter, Maribel Rozzo, clash with Demon Lord Rimuru over their plan to protect mankind by ruling over them. Meanwhile, in El Dorado, Demon Lord Leon works toward goals of his own. The awakening of a new Hero draws near!<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News)\",\"averageScore\":82,\"popularity\":115039,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784296800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"ikxIrDr72iA\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ikxIrDr72iA/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":410303,\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784298600,\"media\":{\"id\":202508,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kami no Shizuku\",\"english\":\"The Drops of God\",\"native\":\"神の雫\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202508-dk6LEyevJYUY.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202508-dk6LEyevJYUY.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e44386\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/202508-K276v0truxE0.jpg\",\"description\":\"World-renowned wine critic Yutaka Kanzaki has passed away, leaving behind a wine collection worth over 12 billion yen. His will states that his collection will be given to the one who can identify the origin and year of twelve wines he’s chosen, the “Twelve Apostles”, and one that’s superior even to them, <i>“The Drops of God”. </i><br><br>\\nCompeting for the prize are Yutaka’s son, Shizuku, who received a world-class education in wine but rebelled against his father and has never drank a drop, and Issei Tomine, a young charismatic wine critic whom Yutaka had recently adopted as his son. <br><br>\\nWhat is wine? What is a parent and a child? What is life?<br>\\nThe complex and fragrant battle surrounding the legendary <i>”Drops of God”</i> is about to begin… <br><br>\\n(Source: Pony Canyon)\",\"averageScore\":54,\"popularity\":5223,\"episodes\":24,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Mystery\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784298600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Oz5EkYVJbBc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Oz5EkYVJbBc/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413705,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784298600,\"media\":{\"id\":188525,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Kore Kaite Shine\",\"english\":\"Draw This, Then Die!\",\"native\":\"これ描いて死ね\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188525-uWhw4rQcqOyF.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188525-uWhw4rQcqOyF.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e48650\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"First-year high school student Ai Yasumi lives on the island of Izu Oshima and loves reading manga. But after a certain turning point, she sets her sights on creating stories of her own! As she dives into the world of manga-making, Ai faces challenges, growth, and the excitement of chasing her creative dreams. Where will her creative journey take her?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":71,\"popularity\":6640,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784298600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"jI61NtGuxV4\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jI61NtGuxV4/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417161,\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784298600,\"media\":{\"id\":182616,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi 2nd Season\",\"english\":\"The Elusive Samurai Season 2\",\"native\":\"逃げ上手の若君 第二期\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182616-ZOCgArw9cgqI.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182616-ZOCgArw9cgqI.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e45050\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182616-kmIqMEUsLYrO.jpg\",\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":18376,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784298600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"5xV6uMwR-Xo\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5xV6uMwR-Xo/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":412183,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784300400,\"media\":{\"id\":203490,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Uchi no Otouto-domo ga Sumimasen\",\"english\":\"Please Excuse My Younger Brothers\",\"native\":\"うちの弟どもがすみません\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203490-YQXiymUiDQNA.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203490-YQXiymUiDQNA.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fef150\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The manga centers on high school student Ito Hazui. During her spring break at the end of her first year of high school, Ito's mother remarries, and Ito moves to live with her new family, becoming Ito Narita. Upon arriving at her new house, Ito is shocked to learn she now has four younger step-brothers. Ito tries her hardest to get along with all of the new members of her family, but the eldest brother Gen is a bit cold to her. However, under his aloof facade, he occasionally shows his kindness.\\n<BR><BR>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"averageScore\":67,\"popularity\":6154,\"episodes\":24,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Romance\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784300400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"P927_ZvgUUg\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/P927_ZvgUUg/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414750,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784304000,\"media\":{\"id\":209983,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Hell Mode: Yarikomi-zuki no Gamer wa Haisettei no Isekai de Musou Suru 2nd Season\",\"english\":\"HELL MODE: The Hardcore Gamer Dominates in Another World with Garbage Balancing Season 2\",\"native\":\"ヘルモード ～やり込み好きのゲーマーは廃設定の異世界で無双する～ 2nd Season\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx209983-sFOcKyqMufxb.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx209983-sFOcKyqMufxb.jpg\",\"color\":\"#0dbbf1\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The second season of <i>Hell Mode</i>.\",\"averageScore\":72,\"popularity\":24381,\"episodes\":13,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784304000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"hr_7R76pUC8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hr_7R76pUC8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414626,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784305800,\"media\":{\"id\":207674,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ushiro no Shoumen Kamui-san\",\"english\":\"KAMUI ---He's behind you\",\"native\":\"うしろの正面カムイさん\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx207674-BT8lFAwH1WrL.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx207674-BT8lFAwH1WrL.jpg\",\"color\":null},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"This exorcism is OMFFFFFFFFF!!!! Shizuka is a self-proclaimed ordinary high school girl who \\\"only\\\" sees ghosts. Using her unique ability to attract spirits, she works as an assistant to the famous psychic, Kamui. Though Kamui boasts overwhelming spiritual power, his exorcism methods are unprecedented...?! Will Shizuka, tossed about by supernatural disturbances, ever find peace? The curtain rises on \\\"supreme\\\" exorcism!! OMFFFFFFFFFG ALMIGHTY!!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: OceanVeil)\",\"averageScore\":55,\"popularity\":11612,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":12,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784305800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"sHlZd-0gI0k\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sHlZd-0gI0k/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417175,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784306520,\"media\":{\"id\":213831,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Snack HAZAMA\",\"english\":\"Snack Hazama\",\"native\":\"スナックはざま-HAZAMA-\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx213831-jrH7JR6feW1q.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213831-jrH7JR6feW1q.png\",\"color\":\"#e48628\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"A weekly mini anime shown with each episode of <i>Ushiro no Shoumen Kamui-san</i>.\",\"averageScore\":52,\"popularity\":598,\"episodes\":12,\"duration\":12,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784306520},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":406456,\"episode\":225,\"airingAt\":1784327400,\"media\":{\"id\":142274,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Ninjala\",\"english\":\"Ninjala the Animation\",\"native\":\"ニンジャラ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png\",\"color\":\"#f1bb43\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The year is 20XX. The ninja, who once forged the history of Japan, were scattered across the country during the Meiji Restoration. As these ninja mingled with the other clans, their bloodline thinned, and they gradually faded from sight. The descendants of these ninja clans, seeking to preserve their heritage, formed the WNA (World Ninja Association) in the hope of carrying on their legacy.\\n<br><br>\\nAnd so it was that the WNA succeeded in developing Ninja-Gum, an art which could summon forth the strength of the Shinobi. And yet creating the most powerful Ninja-Gum requires the strongest of ninja DNA. So it was that the Ninjala Tournament was held, that the mightiest of all ninjas could be found...\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Official Game website)\",\"averageScore\":47,\"popularity\":1395,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Comedy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":2022,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":225,\"airingAt\":1784327400},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413743,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784331000,\"media\":{\"id\":212308,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Pan no Akachan (TV)\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"パンの赤ちゃん\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx212308-HUdh20Djd7cm.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx212308-HUdh20Djd7cm.jpg\",\"color\":\"#1abbd6\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":null,\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":169,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":2,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784331000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"NGwgoL0TvI8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NGwgoL0TvI8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415770,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784334360,\"media\":{\"id\":183231,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Rilakkuma\",\"english\":\"RILAKKUMA\",\"native\":\"リラックマ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b183231-z7SgjmXZBcoX.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b183231-z7SgjmXZBcoX.png\",\"color\":\"#28c9e4\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/183231-JFjTqQe3rPCw.jpg\",\"description\":\"Everyday life gets a cozy twist with the laid-back Rilakkuma. Gentle moments of friendship, change, and small joys unfold, turning ordinary moments into something quietly magical—one soft, comforting day at a time.\\n<br><br>\\nIt's a moment that will make your heart feel lighter and lighter. No matter where you are or what you're doing, Rilakkuma will be by your side. An exciting new story begins! Experience the stress-free world of Rilakkuma, the relaxed bear who makes being lazy look effortless!<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll, Rilakkuma Anime Site, translated)\",\"averageScore\":60,\"popularity\":1499,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":1,\"genres\":[\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV_SHORT\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784334360},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"rV-fcFL5vtU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rV-fcFL5vtU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414698,\"episode\":162,\"airingAt\":1784340000,\"media\":{\"id\":137683,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen\",\"english\":\"Soul Land 2: The Peerless Tang Clan\",\"native\":\"斗罗大陆2绝世唐门\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The Tang Sect in a turbulent world. There is nothing but martial spirit here. Ten thousand years after the founding of the Tang Sect, it is in relative decline. An extremely talented man was born. Can the new Shrek Seven Monsters revive the Tang Sect and bring it back to glory? A soul beast of over one million years old; Electrolux who can pick stars; The new soul utensil system that led to the decline of the Tang Sect... A lot of secrets are to be revealed. Can the secret weapons of the Tang Sect be sharp again? Can the Tang Sect regain its former glory?\\n</br></br>\\n(Source: WeTV)\",\"averageScore\":76,\"popularity\":2800,\"episodes\":182,\"duration\":20,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Romance\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":162,\"airingAt\":1784340000},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":409429,\"episode\":1344,\"airingAt\":1784359800,\"media\":{\"id\":966,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Crayon Shin-chan\",\"english\":\"Shin Chan\",\"native\":\"クレヨンしんちゃん\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e4e428\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/966-J5CwLLTBs4OO.jpg\",\"description\":\"Crayon Shin-chan follows the wacky antics and adventures of five-year-old Shinnosuke \\\"Shin\\\" Nohara and his parents, neighbors, and friends and is set in Kasukabe, Saitama Prefecture, Japan.<br><br>\\nMany of the jokes in the series stem from Shin-chan's occasionally weird, unnatural and inappropriate use of language, as well as from his inappropriate behavior. A typical gag involves Shin-chan confounding his parents by using the wrong phrase for the occasion; for example, saying \\\"Welcome back!\\\" instead of \\\"I am back!\\\" when he comes home.<br><br>\\nDuring the beginning of the series, the TV show was mostly based on the storyline in the original manga. As the show progressed, more and more episodes became anime-original.\",\"averageScore\":77,\"popularity\":19407,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":21,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Ecchi\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":1992,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1344,\"airingAt\":1784359800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":380052,\"episode\":924,\"airingAt\":1784361600,\"media\":{\"id\":8687,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Doraemon (2005)\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"ドラえもん (2005)\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fed628\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/8687-aa3QbJjGfy3B.jpg\",\"description\":\"A new Doraemon series produced by the same team as the 1979 series (in association with Studio Pierrot) with new voice actors and staff and updated character designs.\",\"averageScore\":77,\"popularity\":7545,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2005,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":924,\"airingAt\":1784361600},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416143,\"episode\":14,\"airingAt\":1784363400,\"media\":{\"id\":171110,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Honzuki no Gekokujou: Ryoushu no Youjo\",\"english\":\"Ascendance of a Bookworm: Adopted Daughter of an Archduke\",\"native\":\"本好きの下剋上 領主の養女\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx171110-7zOdInS6DQNL.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx171110-7zOdInS6DQNL.jpg\",\"color\":\"#5daee4\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/171110-lgtmKokpevUM.jpg\",\"description\":\"Anime adaptation of Part 3 of <i>Honzuki no Gekokujou</i>.\\n<br><br>\\nFollowing a disastrous encounter with a noble, Myne finally resolves to say goodbye to her family and friends in the lower city, changing her name to “Rozemyne” and beginning her new life as the adopted daughter of Ehrenfest’s archduke. However, her days as an archnoble in noble society are brutal, as she is put through rigorous etiquette and magic training on top of her duties as High Bishop and forewoman. It all proves too much for a weak little seven-year-old girl... Or it would have, had the High Priest not offered her the keys to the temple’s book room as a reward. If she could get her hands on those, she’d be able to read all sorts of precious books! Her name may have changed, but Rozemyne’s passion for books remains the same as she charges into a whole new world! The detailed setting expands as the printing industry grows in size. Here begins Part 3 of this biblio-fantasy for book lovers everywhere!\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: J-Novel Club)\",\"averageScore\":76,\"popularity\":34883,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Fantasy\",\"Slice of Life\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":14,\"airingAt\":1784363400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"rtPF6rjrdSU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rtPF6rjrdSU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":416568,\"episode\":1207,\"airingAt\":1784365200,\"media\":{\"id\":235,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Meitantei Conan\",\"english\":\"Detective Conan\",\"native\":\"名探偵コナン\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg\",\"color\":\"#28a1e4\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/235-MTmiz0uB0fMd.jpg\",\"description\":\"$29\",\"averageScore\":81,\"popularity\":78132,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Mystery\",\"Psychological\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":1996,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1207,\"airingAt\":1784365200},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":410451,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784366760,\"media\":{\"id\":184492,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mairimashita! Iruma-kun 4\",\"english\":\"Welcome to Demon School! Iruma-kun Season 4\",\"native\":\"魔入りました！入間くん 第4シリーズ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184492-KUVFGieuMaOx.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184492-KUVFGieuMaOx.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1bb28\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/184492-JsZazzn4Acqf.jpg\",\"description\":\"The fourth season of <i>Mairimashita! Iruma-kun.</i>\\n<br><br>\\nSuzuki Iruma and all thirteen students of the Misfit Class must perform to reach Rank 4 at the Music Festival.<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News)\",\"averageScore\":80,\"popularity\":36936,\"episodes\":24,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAir