nilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx213356-nYFTX2yeMBd5.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f19335\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"Second season of <i>Guangyin Zhi Wai</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":229,\"episodes\":52,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":5,\"airingAt\":1784368800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415665,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784376000,\"media\":{\"id\":186863,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Neko to Ryuu\",\"english\":\"The Cat and the Dragon\",\"native\":\"猫と竜\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186863-AO4efoB8HuzA.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186863-AO4efoB8HuzA.png\",\"color\":\"#e4e45d\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/186863-hRsC2yxvILTx.jpg\",\"description\":\"The story follows a fire-breathing, human-hating dragon raised by a mother cat in a forest. The dragon, known affectionately as \\\"Uncle Wing,\\\" watches over the many curious cats — such as one that goes on an adventure with a human prince, and another that lives in the city and people-watches as a hobby — and gradually warms up to humans along the way.<br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll News)<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Each episode streamed 1 week early on ABEMA and dAnimeStore. The original TV broadcast started on July 4, 2026.</i>\",\"averageScore\":74,\"popularity\":15952,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784376000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"xi4rGcyeYr8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xi4rGcyeYr8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414650,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784379600,\"media\":{\"id\":187538,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"BLACK TORCH\",\"english\":\"BLACK TORCH\",\"native\":\"BLACK TORCH\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187538-fXVXKYUA3VV6.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187538-fXVXKYUA3VV6.jpg\",\"color\":\"#435dff\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187538-287evzCezNl0.jpg\",\"description\":\"Jirou Azuma is no average high schooler. A descendant of ninjas and trained in the ancient warrior art of the shinobi, Jirou is also able to talk with animals. After a mysterious encounter with an injured cat named Ragou, Jirou discovers the feline is actually the legendary Black Star of Doom! Joined by the Bureau of Espionage, they fight off swarms of mononoke lying in wait to exploit Ragou’s powers.\\n<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":73,\"popularity\":42238,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Sci-Fi\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784379600},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"2clp09dITKY\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2clp09dITKY/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415214,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784381400,\"media\":{\"id\":206249,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Iwamoto-senpai no Suisen\",\"english\":\"Recommendations from Iwamoto-Senpai\",\"native\":\"岩元先輩ノ推薦\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206249-1AUSry416wGz.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206249-1AUSry416wGz.png\",\"color\":\"#fed650\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/206249-gKJUJDCbMjDT.jpg\",\"description\":\"The year 1910. Iwamoto Kodou is a young boy who has successfully carried out many curious missions under the military's directive. His destinations lead to encounters with the strange, weaving tales of history that have yet to be told.\",\"averageScore\":54,\"popularity\":4892,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784381400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"5Q2OFIvOME0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5Q2OFIvOME0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":414431,\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784385000,\"media\":{\"id\":190569,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Tenmaku no Jaadugar\",\"english\":\"Jaadugar: A Witch in Mongolia\",\"native\":\"天幕のジャードゥーガル\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx190569-KnCQLI3Z8hPX.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx190569-KnCQLI3Z8hPX.jpg\",\"color\":\"#50a1e4\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/190569-fQrApHKs9PIz.jpg\",\"description\":\"After losing her mother and her homeland, Sitara’s despair transforms into determination with the power of knowledge. New possibilities unfold when a family of scholars takes her in, deepening her education. Meanwhile, Genghis Khan’s Mongol Empire conquers nation after nation, nearing Sitara’s new home. After the Fourth Prince of the empire takes her captive, a flame of revenge is ignited.<br><br>\\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\",\"averageScore\":80,\"popularity\":27639,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":23,\"genres\":[\"Drama\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":4,\"airingAt\":1784385000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"GBHYXPp1lt8\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GBHYXPp1lt8/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415870,\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784385000,\"media\":{\"id\":195600,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Yomi no Tsugai\",\"english\":\"Daemons of the Shadow Realm\",\"native\":\"黄泉のツガイ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx195600-moI0UFArtOme.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx195600-moI0UFArtOme.jpg\",\"color\":\"#e49335\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/195600-UxHvDXwzJxlP.jpg\",\"description\":\"In a remote mountain village under the watchful eyes of two stone guardians, the young Yuru contentedly lives off the land while staying close to the only family he has left—Asa, his precious twin sister. Asa, meanwhile, carries out a mysterious “duty” on behalf of the village while locked in a cage. Why is Asa a prisoner? And what other secrets does Yuru’s otherwise idyllic home hide?\\n<br><br>(Source: Square Enix)\",\"averageScore\":78,\"popularity\":117983,\"episodes\":24,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Comedy\",\"Fantasy\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784385000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"XCyj9KKKjUI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XCyj9KKKjUI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417319,\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784385960,\"media\":{\"id\":196012,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"MAO\",\"english\":\"MAO\",\"native\":\"MAO\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196012-R3YNjunufpYh.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196012-R3YNjunufpYh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1935d\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196012-BbzGv8DuqVah.jpg\",\"description\":\"<b>A curse that binds past and present.</b>\\n<br><br>\\nMao, a young mystic who lives in the Taisho period of early 1900s Japan, is a mysterious onmyoji who, after suffering a life-altering curse, has continued to live for nine hundred long years. His world becomes even stranger when he meets Nanoka Kiba, a junior high schooler who seems to have traveled from the future. In spite of her tender years, Nanoka has lived a strange life herself, marked by her traumatic experience as a young child losing both her parents to a grisly accident. But when Nanoka decides to return to that fateful shopping arcade, she is transported to another time and place - a world where supernatural ayakashi thrive in an era long before her own. There she meets Mao, whose abrupt and bizarre question prompts Nanoka to see herself and her curious life in a completely new light. Now the two travelers from different worlds unite as they take on the dark powers that grip both their lives.\\n<br><br>(Source: VIZ Media, Hulu, edited)\",\"averageScore\":65,\"popularity\":17400,\"episodes\":26,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Mystery\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784385960},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"eVfpoS0rjw0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eVfpoS0rjw0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":417320,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784385960,\"media\":{\"id\":196012,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"MAO\",\"english\":\"MAO\",\"native\":\"MAO\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196012-R3YNjunufpYh.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196012-R3YNjunufpYh.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1935d\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196012-BbzGv8DuqVah.jpg\",\"description\":\"<b>A curse that binds past and present.</b>\\n<br><br>\\nMao, a young mystic who lives in the Taisho period of early 1900s Japan, is a mysterious onmyoji who, after suffering a life-altering curse, has continued to live for nine hundred long years. His world becomes even stranger when he meets Nanoka Kiba, a junior high schooler who seems to have traveled from the future. In spite of her tender years, Nanoka has lived a strange life herself, marked by her traumatic experience as a young child losing both her parents to a grisly accident. But when Nanoka decides to return to that fateful shopping arcade, she is transported to another time and place - a world where supernatural ayakashi thrive in an era long before her own. There she meets Mao, whose abrupt and bizarre question prompts Nanoka to see herself and her curious life in a completely new light. Now the two travelers from different worlds unite as they take on the dark powers that grip both their lives.\\n<br><br>(Source: VIZ Media, Hulu, edited)\",\"averageScore\":65,\"popularity\":17400,\"episodes\":26,\"duration\":25,\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Mystery\",\"Romance\",\"Supernatural\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":15,\"airingAt\":1784385960},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"eVfpoS0rjw0\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eVfpoS0rjw0/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":413159,\"episode\":14,\"airingAt\":1784386800,\"media\":{\"id\":211181,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Mu Shen Ji 4\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"牧神记4\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx211181-93dehu3v5xHE.png\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx211181-93dehu3v5xHE.png\",\"color\":\"#d6ae6b\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The fourth part of <i>Mu Shen Ji</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":305,\"episodes\":26,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":null,\"seasonYear\":null,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":14,\"airingAt\":1784386800},\"trailer\":null,\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415387,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784386800,\"media\":{\"id\":196017,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Grow Up Show: Himawari no Circus-dan\",\"english\":\"Grow Up Show\",\"native\":\"グロウアップショウ ～ひまわりのサーカス団～\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196017-GynDNdbDzqzk.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196017-GynDNdbDzqzk.jpg\",\"color\":\"#f1ae1a\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The anime's story is set in the late 1950s and early 1960s, during the height of Japan's economic boom, when the circus is a major form of entertainment. Different circus troupes travel throughout Japan to perform and compete for a chance to participate in the world-renowned festival called \\\"Circus Collection.\\\" One troupe called the \\\"Sunflower Circus,\\\" led by its ringmaster Maria, travels around Japan to perform, despite struggling with financial difficulties. However, they meet a circus prodigy named Mizuka Tsurumaki. This is the story of a one-of-a-kind circus show of young girls with big dreams.<br><br>\\n(Source: Anime News Network)\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":6088,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784386800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"PAneuhZLHzU\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/PAneuhZLHzU/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415578,\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784386800,\"media\":{\"id\":196223,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Cyborg 009: Nemesis\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"サイボーグ009 ネメシス\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196223-IGxBuIsascyV.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196223-IGxBuIsascyV.jpg\",\"color\":\"#3586ff\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"To commemorate the 61st anniversary of the original manga's debut: a new anime based on Shoutarou Ishinomori's <i>Cyborg 009</i>.\",\"averageScore\":null,\"popularity\":789,\"episodes\":3,\"duration\":30,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"ONA\",\"season\":\"SUMMER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"NOT_YET_RELEASED\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":1,\"airingAt\":1784386800},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"Da_2mAvLs5E\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Da_2mAvLs5E/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415568,\"episode\":3,\"airingAt\":1784388600,\"media\":{\"id\":194219,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Oni no Hanayome\",\"english\":\"The Ogre's Bride\",\"native\":\"鬼の花嫁\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b194219-56EhyK775lga.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b194219-56EhyK775lga.jpg\",\"color\":\"#ff7835\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"A Japanese-style ayakashi Cinderella story! <i>\\\"You're the bride I've been searching for all this time.\\\"</i> The ayakashi and humans coexist in harmony. The ayakashi, having superior abilities and beautiful appearances, sometimes find their partner among human women, making them their \\\"bride\\\". The bride, in exchange for bringing prosperity, receives absolute love from the ayakashi. Yuzu is constantly compared to her sister, a bride of a demon fox, and is resented by her family every day. One day, when Yuzu just couldn't take things anymore, a man appears before her on a bridge. This man is the most beautiful man Yuzu has ever seen... and he's calling her his wife?! <i>\\\"Just be quiet and let me hold you.\\\"</i> The most powerful, \\\"cold-hearted\\\" ayakashi is pouring his heart out for Yuzu?!<br><br>\\n(Source: MangaPlaza)\",\