",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg\",\"color\":\"#d6ae1a\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/202957-B9U0hNv2Dqap.jpg\",\"description\":\"The 23rd installment of the long-running <i>Precure</i> series.<br>\\n<br>\\nAnna Akechi is a second-year junior high student living in Makoto Mirai Town. On her 14th birthday, she has a chance encounter with a fairy named Pochitan, and a magical pendant caused her to travel back in time from 2027 to 1999! In the Makoto Mirai Town 28 years in the past, Anna meets Mikuru Kobayashi, a girl her age who wants to become a great detective.<br>\\n<br>\\nMeanwhile, people in town are in trouble as their prized possessions are being stolen from under their noses - the cause being a group of Phantom Thieves. To stop them, Anna and Mikuru turn into Precures! Maybe if they solve these mysteries, Anna can find her way back to her own time?<br>\\n<br>\\n(Source: Official Website, translated)\",\"averageScore\":74,\"popularity\":5545,\"episodes\":51,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Mahou Shoujo\",\"Mystery\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"WINTER\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":25,\"airingAt\":1784417400},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"qjozo1fh7OI\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qjozo1fh7OI/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":415931,\"episode\":39,\"airingAt\":1784419200,\"media\":{\"id\":188388,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\",\"english\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\",\"native\":\"DIGIMON BEATBREAK\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg\",\"color\":\"#fec928\"},\"bannerImage\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/188388-kCSxLPMY2JkD.jpg\",\"description\":\"<i>GLITCH THE FUTURE.</i><br><br>\\n\\nTomoro Tenma lives in a world where human thoughts and emotions—known as “e-Pulse”—power AI devices called Sapotama. But when Digimon begin materializing from Sapotama and feeding on e-Pulse, society begins to fracture. After Gekkomon appears from his device, Tomoro joins Glowing Dawn, a secret team investigating rogue Digimon and the dark truth of a system both fueled and corrupted by emotion. What new future will be forged by humans and Digimon? <br><br>\\n\\n(Source: Crunchyroll, DIGIMON BEATBREAK Official Site, edited)\",\"averageScore\":68,\"popularity\":13846,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":24,\"genres\":[\"Action\",\"Adventure\",\"Fantasy\",\"Sci-Fi\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"FALL\",\"seasonYear\":2025,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":39,\"airingAt\":1784419200},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"naNctHU5MQE\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/naNctHU5MQE/hqdefault.jpg\"},\"isAdult\":false}},{\"id\":410144,\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784421000,\"media\":{\"id\":206523,\"title\":{\"romaji\":\"Onegai AiPri\",\"english\":null,\"native\":\"おねがいアイプリ\"},\"coverImage\":{\"extraLarge\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx206523-2IaJCk4R7i63.jpg\",\"large\":\"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx206523-2IaJCk4R7i63.jpg\",\"color\":\"#0035ff\"},\"bannerImage\":null,\"description\":\"The latest entry in the <i>Pretty Series</i> franchise and a new chapter in the <i>AiPri</i> series.\\n<br><br>\\n<i>Note: Relations are provisional and will be updated when more info is announced.</i>\",\"averageScore\":54,\"popularity\":729,\"episodes\":null,\"duration\":null,\"genres\":[\"Music\"],\"format\":\"TV\",\"season\":\"SPRING\",\"seasonYear\":2026,\"status\":\"RELEASING\",\"nextAiringEpisode\":{\"episode\":16,\"airingAt\":1784421000},\"trailer\":{\"id\":\"j5MgjyhhUBc\",\"site\":\"youtube\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/j5Mgj